hadiths[316]{hadithnumber,text}:
5979,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us (deen ya khilaafat) ke mamley mein log Quraish ke tabey hain, un (logon) ke musalman, Quraishi musalmanon ke tabey hain, aur un (aam logon) ke kafir, un (Quraish ke) kafiron ke tabey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5980,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log khair (Islam) aur shar (kufr) mein Quraish ke tabey hain.'' rawahu Muslim.
5981,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye maamla (khilaafat) Quraish mein rahega jab tak un mein do aadmi bhi baqi rahen.'' muttafaq aleh.
5982,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''ye khilaafat Quraish mein rahegi jab tak wo Deen ko qaaim rakhengey, aur jo shakhs unki mukhalifat kerega Allah usey chehrey ke bal ondha karkey zaleel kar dega.'' Bukhari."
5983,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' baara khaleefaon tak Islam ghalib rahega aur wo sab Quraish se hongey.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''logon ke maamlat sahih aur durust chaltey rahengey jab tak baara aadmi unke hukmran rahengey, wo sab Quraish se hongey.'' eik aur riwayat mein hai : ''qiyamat tak Deen qaaim rahega aur un par baara khaleefaa hongey aur wo sab Quraish se hongey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5984,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qabeela ghifaar jo hai, Allah ne unhen maaf farma diya, qabila Aslam ko Allah ne salaamat rakha aur jo qabila usba hai usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki.'' muttafaq aleh."
5985,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Quraish , ansaar , juhaina , muzena , Aslam , ghifaar aur ashja' qabiley merey himayati hain, aur Allah aur uskey Rasool ke siwa unka koi himayati nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
5986,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aslam , ghifaar , muzena , aur juhaina qabiley , bano Tameem aur bano Aamir qabeelon se behtar hain, aur wo do haleefon banu-Asad aur ghatfaan se bhi behtar hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5987,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine bano Tameem ke mutalliq jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se teen khaslatein suni hain, tab se main unhen mehbub rakhta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se wo dajjaal par sab se ziyada sakht hongey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, unke sadqaat aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye hamari qom ke sadqaat hain.'' aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas unke kuchh qaidi they, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen azad kar do kyonkey wo Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein se hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5988,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quraish ki ihaanat (tauheen) karna chahega Allah uski ihaanat aur zaleel karega.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5989,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! to ne (Badr aur ehzaab mein) Quraish ke pehley afrad ko azab mein mubtala kiya, to unke baad walon ko inaam ata farma.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5990,"Hazrat Abu-Aamir Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Asad aur Ash'ar qabiley achchhey hain, wo maidane-jihad se farar hotey hain na khayanat kartey hain, wo mujh se hain aur main un se hun.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5991,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Azad qabila zamin par Allah ka lashkar hai, log chahtey hain ke wo unhen neecha dikhayen lekin Allah ne is baat ka inkar farma diya hai, wo unhen rifat (bulandi) hi ata farmata hai, logon par eik aisa waqt bhi aaeyga ke aadmi khahish kerega ke kaash! mera walid azdi hota aur kaash! meri walida azdi hoti.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5992,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat paai to wo teen qabeelon ko napasand farmatey they, Saqif, bano Haneefa aur bano Umayya. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5993,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Saqif (qabiley) main eik shakhs kazaab (jhuta) aur eik zalim hoga.'' Abdullah bin Isma ne kaha : kazaab se murad Mukhtaar bin Abi Ubaid aur zalim se murad HUjjaj bin Yusuf hai, Hisham bin Hassan ne kaha : Hujjaj ne jin afrad ko baandh kar qatl kiya unki tadaad eik lakh bees hazar tak pahunchti hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5994,"Hazrat Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sahih Muslim mein riwayat kiya hai, jab Hujjaj ne Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko qatl kiya to Asma (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hadees bayan ki ke Saqif qabiley main eik kazaab aur eik zalim hoga. raha kazaab to ham ne usey dekh liya aur raha zalim to mera khayal hai ke ye wohi hai. rawahu Muslim. aur mukammal hadees teesri fasal mein aaeygi."
5995,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Saqif qabiley ke teeron ne hamen jala kar rakh diya hai, aap unke liye Allah se badduaa farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Saqif qabiley ko hidayat ata farma.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5996,"Hazrat Abdur-Razzaaq , apney walid sey, wo Meena'a se aur wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas they ke aadmi aap ke paas aaya mera khayal hai Qais qabiley se tha, usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Hameer qabiley par lanat farmaeyn, aapney us se aeraz farmaya (andekha) , phir wo dusri janib se aaya to aapney us se aeraz farmaya , phir wo dusri janib se aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se aeraz farmaya , neez (isi ke saath) farmaya : ''Allah Hameer par rehem farmaai , unke munh salam kartey hain, unke haath khana khilatey hain, aur wo aman aur amaan waley hain.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur ham usey sirf Abdur-Razzaaq ke tareeq se pehchantey hain, aur is Meena'a se munkir hadise riwayat ki jati hain. rawahu Tirmizi."
5997,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''tum kis qabiley se ho?'' maine arz kya, dos sey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main nahin samajhta tha ke dos qabiley ke kisi shakhs mein bhalai ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5998,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''mujhey naraz na karna warna tum apney Deen se nikal jaaogey.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main aap ko kaisey naraz kar sakta hun, aap ki wajeh se Allah ne hamein hidayat nasib farmaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Arbon se dushmani rakhogey to tum mujh se dushmani rakhogey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5999,"Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney Arbon ko faraib diya to wo meri shafaat mein dakhil hoga na usey meri muwaddat nasib hogi.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. ham is hadees ko sirf Husain bin umr ke tareeq se pehchantey hain, aur wo muhaddeseen ke nazdik qawi nahin. rawahu Tirmizi."
6000,"Hazrat Talha bin Malik ki azaad karda londi Umme-Hareer bayan karti hain, maine apney maalik ko bayan kartey huey suna, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''arbon ki halakat qiyamat ke qareeb hone ki alamat hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6001,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khilaafat Quraish mein hai, qaza Ansaar mein , Azan habshiyon mein aur amanat Azad yani Yamen mein hai.'' ye riwayat moquf hai, Imam Tirmizi ne isey riwayat kiya, aur farmaya : iska moquf hona ziyada sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6002,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mutee apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, maine Fateh Makka ke roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''us roz ke baad roze-qiyamat tak kisi Quraishi ko baandh kar qatl na kiya jaey.'' rawahu Muslim."
6003,"Hazrat Abu Nofal Muawiya bin Muslim bayan kartey hain, maine Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madiney ki ghaati par (sooli par lataktey huey) dekha, Quraishi aur doosrey log unke paas se guzartey rahey yahan tak ke Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas se guzrey aur wahan thehar kar farmaya : Abu khubaib ! tum par salam , Abu khubaib ! tum par salam , Abu khubaib ! tum par salam , Allah ki qism ! kya main tumhen is (khilaafat ke maamley) se mana nahin karta tha, Allah ki qism ! kya maine tumhen is se mana nahin kiya tha? Allah ki qism ! main tumhen bahut rozey rakhney wala, bahut ziyada qiyam karney wala aur sila rehmi karney wala hi janta hun, sun lo ! Allah ki qism ! jo log tujhey bura khayal kartey hain haqiqat mein wo khud burey hain. eik dusri riwayat mein hai, (jo tumhen bura samajhtey hain kya) wo log achchhey hain? phir Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) chaley gaey, Hujjaj ko Abdullah ka mauqif aur unki baat pahunchi to usney unhen bula bheja, un (Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu)) ko sooli se utaar diya gaya aur unhen yahudiyon ke qabristaan mein dal diya gaya. phir Hujjaj ne unki walida Asma binte-Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja to unhoney aaney se inkar kar diya, phir usney dobara pegham bheja ke aap aa jaeyn warna mein aisey shakhs ko bhejunga jo tumhen baalon se pakad kar ghaseet layega, raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney inkar kiya aur kaha, Allah ki qism ! main terey paas nahin aaungi yahan tak ke to us shakhs ko merey paas bhejey jo merey baalon se pakad kar mujhey ghasitey, raawi bayan kartey hain, Hujjaj ne kaha : merey jootey mujhey do , usney apney jootey pehney aur tez tez chalta hua un tak pahunch gaya, aur kaha : bataao ! Allah ke dushman ke sath maine kaisa sulook kiya? Asma (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main samajhti hun ke tu ney Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki duniya kharab ki aur usney teri aakhirat barbad kar di. mujhey pata chala hai ke to (tohin ke andaz mein) usey ذات النطاقین  (do izaar wali) ka beta kehta hai, Allah ki qism ! main ذات النطاقین hun, un (izaar bandon) mein se eik ke sath mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke khaney ko chopayon se bachaney ke liye , aur raha doosra to us se koi bhi aurat be niaz nahin ho sakti, sun lo ! ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hadees bayan farmaee ke'' Saqif main eik kazaab aur eik zalim hoga.'' raha kazaab to ham usey dekh chukey, aur raha zalim to mera khayal hai ke wo tum hi ho. raawi bayan kartey hain, wo unke paas se chala gaya aur phir unke paas dobara nahin aaya. rawahu Muslim."
6004,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke fitney se pehley do aadmi ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur unhoney kaha : logon ne jo kuch kiya aap usey dekh rahey hain aur aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke bete aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi hain, aap ko nikalney se kon si chiz maane (rukawat) hai? unhoney farmaya : merey liye ye chiz maane (rukawat) thi ke Allah ne musalman ko qatl karna mujh par haram qarar diya hai, un dono ne kaha : kya Allah Taala ne ye nahin farmaya : ''un se qitaal karo yahan tak ke fitna khatam ho jaey.'' ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham ne qitaal kiya yahan tak ke fitna (shirk) khatam ho gaya aur Deen khalis Allah ke liye ho gaya, aur tum chahtey ho ke tum lado yahan tak ke fitna paida ho aur Deen ghair Allah ke liye ho jaey. Bukhari."
6005,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Tufail bin Amr Dosi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney arz kiya : dos qabila halak ho gaya, usney nafarmani ki aur inkar kiya, aap unke liye badduaa karen, logon ne samjha ke aap unke liye badduaa karengey. lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! dos ko hidayat nasib farma aur unhen (musalman bana kar) ley aa.'' muttafaq aleh."
6006,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''arbon ke sath teen khaslaton ki wajeh se mohabbat karo, kyonkey mein Arbi hun, Quran Arbi (zaban mein) hai aur ehle jannat ka kalam Arbi mein hoga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
6007,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey Sahaba ko bura mat kaho , kyonkey agar tum mein se koi shakhs uhad pahad ke barabar sona kharch kar daley to wo un mein se kisi eik ke mud (taqreeban siwa chhe so giraam) kharch karney ko pahunch sakta hai na uskey nisf (aadhe) mud ko.'' muttafaq aleh."
6008,"Hazrat Abu-Barda apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, aap yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna sar Mubarak aasman ki taraf uthaya , aur aap aksar apna sar Mubarak aasman ki taraf uthaya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sitarey aasman ki hifazat ka baais hain, jab sitarey jatey rahengey to aasman wade ke mutabiq toot phoot jaeyga, aur main apney Sahaba ki hifazat ka baais hun, jab main chala jaaunga to merey Sahaba ko un fitnon ka samna hoga jis ka un se wada hai, aur merey Sahaba meri ummat ki hifazat ka baais hain, jab merey Sahaba jatey rahengey to meri ummat mein wo chizen (bad-duaa waghera) aa jaeyngi jin ka un se wada kiya ja raha hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
6009,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon par eik aisa waqt aaeyga ke logon ki jamaaten jihad kerengi, un se kaha jaeyga : kya tum mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka koi sahabi bhi hai? wo kahengey : haan , unhen Fateh hogi , phir logon par eik aisa waqt aaeyga ke logon ki jamaaten jihad kerengi to un se puchha jaeyga : kya tum mein koi aisa hai jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki ho? wo kahengey haan , to unhen Fateh hasil hogi . phir logon par eik aisa waqt aaeyga ke logon ki jamaaten jihad kerengi , un se puchha jaeyga : kya tum mein koi tubba taabe'in hai? wo kahengey : haan , to unhen Fateh hasil hogi .'' aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : '' logon par eik aisa waqt aaeyga ke un mein se eik lashkar bheja jaeyga to un se kaha jaeyga : dekho , kya tum apney sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka koi sahabi paatey ho? eik sahabi mil jaeyga to unhen Fateh nasib ho jaeygi, phir doosra lashkar bheja jaeyga, to un se kaha jaeyga : kya un mein koi aisa shakhs hai jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ko dekha ho? unhen Fateh hasil hogi . phir teesra lashkar bheja jaeyga, to kaha jaeyga : dekho , kya tum mein koi aisa shakhs hai jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ko dekha ho? phir chotha lashkar hoga, kaha jaeyga : kya tum un mein kisi aisey shakhs ko dekhtey ho jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ko dekhney waley shakhs ko dekha ho, aisa shakhs mil jaeyga to unhen Fateh hasil ho jaeygi.'' muttafaq aleh."
6010,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ka sab se behtareen zamana mera zamana hai, phir un logon ka jo unke baad aaeyngey , phir wo jo unke baad aaeyngey , phir unke baad aisey log aaeyngey jo gawahi talab kiye baghair gawahi dengey , wo khayanat karengey , aur un par aitimad nahin kiya jaeyga, wo nazar maanengey lekin puri nahin karengey, aur un mein motaapaa aam ho jaeyga.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''wo half talab kiye baghair half uthaeyngey.'' muttafaq aleh."
6011,Aur Sahih Muslim mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai : ''phir aisey log ja-nashin banengey jo motaapey ko pasand karengey.'' rawahu Muslim.
6012,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey Sahaba ki izzat karo, kyonkey wo tum mein se sab se behtar hain, phir wo jo unke baad aaeyngey, phir wo jo unke baad aaeyngey , phir jhoot aam ho jaeyga yahan tak ke aadmi half (qasam) talab kiye baghair half (qasam) uthaega, gawahi talab kiye baghair gawahi dega, sun lo ! jo shakhs jannat ke wast (beech) mein maqam hasil karna pasand karta hai wo jamaat ke sath laga rahey, kyonkey munfarid (tanha) shakhs ke sath shetan hota hai aur wo do afrad se (eik ki nisbat) ziyada door hota hai, aur koi aadmi kisi aurat ke sath khilwat ikhtiyar na karey kyonkey teesra unka shetan hota hai, aur jis shakhs ko uski neki khush kar dey aur uski burai usey buri lagey to wo momin hai.'' (rawahu Nasai fi اکبریٰ)."
6013,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us musalman ko , jisney mujhey dekha ya us shakhs ko dekha jisney mujhey dekha, jahannam ki aag nahin chhuegi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6014,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke (huqooq ke) mutalliq Allah se bar-bar dartey rehna, merey baad unhen nishana mat banana, jis shakhs ne un se mohabbat ki to usney meri mohabbat ke baais un se mohabbat ki, aur jisney un se dushmani rakhi to usney merey sath dushmani rakhney ki wajeh se un se dushmani rakhi, jis shakhs ne unko aziyat (pareshani) pahunchaai, usney mujhey aziyat pahunchaai aur jisney mujhey aziyat pahunchaai , usney Allah ko aziyat pahunchaai, qarib hai ke wo usko (duniya mein) pakad ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6015,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein merey Sahaba ki misal is tarah hai jis tarah khaney mein namak , aur khana namak ke sath hi behtar (lazeez) banta hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah). Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : hamara namak to ja chuka to ham kis tarah sanwar saktey hain?"
6016,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera koi sahabi jis sarzameen par faut hoga to wo qiyamat ke din un logon ka qaaid aur Noor bin kar uthaya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se (لا یبلغنی احد) marwi (bayan) hadees (باب حفظ اللسان) mein zikr ki gaee hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6017,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum aisey logon ko dekho jo merey Sahaba ko bura kehtey hon to tum kaho : tumharey shar par Allah ki lanat ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6018,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : maine apney rab se. apney baad apney Sahaba ke ikhtilaf ke mutalliq puchha to usney meri taraf ""wahi"" farmaee : ''Muhammad ! aap ke Sahaba merey nazdik aasman ke sitaron ki manind hain, un mein se baaz , baaz se ziyada qawi hain, aur her eik ki roshni hai, aur jis shakhs ne bawajud unke ikhtilaf ke jin par wo hain, amal kiya to wo merey nazdik hidayat par hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey Sahaba sitaron ki manind hain, tum un mein se jiski bhi iqtida (pairvi) karogey hidayat pa jaaogey.'' rawahu rizeen."
6019,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''waqt aur maal sirf karney ke lihaz se Abu-Bakar ka mujh par sab se ziyada ehsan hai.'' aur Sahih Bukhari mein lafz (Abu-Bakr) hai.'' aur agar main kisi ko khaleel (jigri dost) banata to main laziman Abu-Bakar ko khaleel banata , lekin ukhuwat (bhaai-chaara) Islaami aur uski muwaddat aur mohabbat kafi hai, masjid mein khulney waley tamam darwazey band kar diye jaeyn albatta Abu-Bakar ka darwaza rehney do.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''agar main apney rab ke siwa kisi aur ko dost banata to main Abu-Bakar ko dost banata.'' muttafaq aleh."
6020,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main kisi ko khaleel (jigri dost) banata to main Abu-Bakar ko dost banata , lekin wo merey bhai aur merey sathi hain aur Allah tumharey sathi ko khaleel bana chuka hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
6021,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney marz mein mujhey farmaya : ''apney walid Abu-Bakar aur apney bhai ko merey paas bulaao yahan tak ke main tehreer likh dun, mujhey andesha hai ke koi tamanna karney wala tamanna karey aur koi kehney wala kahe ke main khilaafat ka mustahiq hun, halanke Allah aur tamam momin sirf Abu-Bakar ko hi qubul karengey.'' rawahu Muslim. aur kitabul humaidi mein (أنا ولا) ki jagah : (أنا اولی) ke alfaz hain."
6022,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai to usney kisi maamle mein aap se baat ki to aapney usey dobara apni khidmat mein hazir honey ka hukm farmaya , usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn ke agar main aaun aur aap ko na paaon, goya us se murad (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki) wafat thi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum mujhey na paao to phir Abu-Bakar ke paas aana.'' muttafaq aleh."
6023,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-zaat-salasil main eik lashkar ka ameer bana kar bheja , wo bayan kartey hain, main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya, aap ko sab se ziyada mohabbat kis se hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha se.'' maine arz kiya : mardon mein se? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey walid (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) se.'' maine arz kiya : phir kis se? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umar se.'' aapney kaee aadmi giney, (ke uskey baad falan , phir falan . . . .) phir main us andeshey ke peshe-nazar ke aap mujhey un mein se sab se aakhir mein na ley jaeyn, khamosh ho gaya. muttafaq aleh."
6024,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Hanfiya bayan kartey hain, maine apney walid se kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad sab se behtar shakhs kon hai? unhoney farmaya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu). maine puchha : phir kon? unhoney farmaya : umr (Raziallahu anhu). aur is andeshe ke peshe-nazar ke aap Usman (Raziallahu anhu) keh dengey, maine kaha : phir aap? unhoney farmaya : main to eik aam musalman hun. Bukhari."
6025,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke barabar kisi ko qarar nahin detey they, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) phir ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba (ki baham (aapas mein) fazilat ki behes) ko tarak kar detey they aur ham un mein se kisi eik ko doosrey par fazilat nahin detey they. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat hai : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hayaat mubaraka mein kaha kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat mein aap ke baad sab se afzal Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Bukhari aur Abu-Dawood."
6026,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ilawa jis shakhs ne ham par koi ehsan kiya tha ham ne uska badla chuka diya hai, lekin unhoney jo kuchh hamein ata kiya hai, uski jaza roze-qiyamat Allah hi unhen ata farmaeyga. aur kisi shakhs ke maal ne mujhey itna faeyda nahin pahunchaya jitna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke maal ne mujhey faeyda pahunchaya hai, agar maine kisi shakhs ko khaleel (jigri dost) banana hota to main Abu-Bakar ko khaleel banata , sun lo ! tumhara sahiab , Allah ka khaleel hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6027,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey sardar hain, ham sab se behtar hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ham sab se ziyada piyarey hain. rawahu Tirmizi."
6028,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''tum merey ghaar ke sathi ho, aur hoz par merey sathi hogey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6029,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ki mojudgi mein kisi aur shakhs ke liye munasib nahin ke wo unki imaamat karaaey.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6030,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein sadqa karney ka hukm farmaya , us waqt merey paas maal bhi tha, maine (dil mein) kaha : agar ho saka to main aaj Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) par sabqat ley jaaunga, wo bayan kartey hain, main apna nisf (aadha) maal lekar hazir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney ghar walon ke liye kya chhod kar aaye ho?'' maine arz kya : itna hi (yani nisf) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apna sara asaasa lekar hazir ho gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ! apney ghar walon ke liye kya chhod kar aaye ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : unke liye Allah aur uskey Rasool (ki raza) chhod kar aaya hun, main (umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main kisi chiz mein un se kabhi bhi sabqat hasil nahin kar sakta. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
6031,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aap aag se Allah ke azad karda (Ateequllah) hain.'' us roz se unka naam (laqab) Ateeq rakh diya gaya. rawahu Tirmizi.
6032,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se pehley mujhey qabr se uthaya jaeyga, phir Abu-Bakar ko , phir umr ko phir main ehle Baqee ke paas aaunga to wo merey sath jama kiye jaeyngey, phir main ehle-Makka ka intizar karunga yahan tak ke main Harmain ke darmiyan jama kiya jaaunga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6033,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael merey paas aaye to unhoney mujhey haath se pakda aur mujhey jannat ka wo darwaza dikhaya jis se meri ummat dakhil hogi.'' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main chahta hun ke main bhi aap ke sath hota yahan tak ke main usey dekh leta, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! Abu-Bakar ! meri ummat mein se sab se pehley jannat mein dakhil honey waley tum hi to ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
6034,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unke paas Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka tazkira kiya gaya to wo ro padey aur kaha : main chahta hun ke merey sarey amal unke dinon (dino) mein se eik yoam (din) aur unki raaton mein se eik raat ki jaise ho jaeyn, rahi unki raat, to wo raat jab unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghaar ki taraf safar kiya tha, jab wo dono wahan tak pahunchey to Abu-Bakar ne arz kiya, Allah ki qism ! aap is mein dakhil nahin hongey yahan tak ke main aap se pehley dakhil ho jaaun, ta ke agar is mein koi chiz ho to uska nuqsan mujhey pahunchey aap us se mehfooz rahen, wo is mein dakhil huye, usey saaf kiya, aur unhoney uski eik janib surakh dekhey, unhoney apna izaar phada aur us se suraakhon ko band kiya, magar do surakh baqi reh gaey aur unhoney un par apney paaon rakh diye, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, tashrif ley ayen, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) andar tashrif ley aaye aur apna sar Mubarak unki god mein rakh kar so gaey, surakh se Abu-Bakar ka paaon das liya gaya, lekin unhoney us andeshe ke peshe-nazar ke aap bedaar na ho jaeyn harkat na ki, unke aansu Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chehre Mubarak par girey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ! kya hua?'' unhoney arz kiya, merey waliden aap par fidaa hon mujhey das liya gaya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne luaab lagaya aur takleef jati rahi, aur baad iske us zahar ka asar un par dobara shuru ho gaya aur yehi unki wafat ka sabab bana , raha unka din to jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai kuchh Arab murtad ho gaey aur unhoney kaha : ham Zakat nahin dengey, unhoney farmaya : agar unhoney eik rassi bhi deney se inkar kiya to main un se jihad karunga. maine kaha : Rasulullah ke khalifa ! logon ko milaaein aur narmi karen, unhoney mujhey farmaya : kya jahiliyat mein sakht they aur Islam mein buzdil ho gaey ho, ""wahi"" ka silsila munqata' khatm ho gaya, Deen mukammal ho chuka, to kya merey jeetey huey Deen kam (naqis) ho jaeyga? rawahu Rizeen."
6035,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum se pehli ummaton mein muhaddis (jinhen ilhaam hota ho) hua kartey they, agar meri ummat mein koi shakhs (muhaddis) hota to wo umr hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
6036,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaney ki ijazat talab ki, us waqt aap ke paas Quraish ki chand khawatin (aap ki paak biviyan) thin, wo aap se buland aawaz mein guftgu kar rahin thin aur aap se naan aur nafqa (bharan-poshan) mein izaafey ka mutalba kar rahi thin, jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ijazat talab ki to wo khadi huin aur jaldi se pardey mein chali gaeen, umr (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans rahey they, unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah aap ko sada khush rakhey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey un par tajjub hai ke wo merey paas thin, jab unhoney aap ki aawaz suni to wo fauran hijaab mein chali gaeen.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : apni jaan ki dushmanon ! tum mujh se darti ho lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se nahin darti ho, unhoney farmaya : haan , aap sakht mizaj aur sakht dil hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ibne Khattab ! aur kuchh kaho , us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! shetan tumhen kisi raastey par chalta mil jata hai to wo us raastey ko chhod kar kisi doosrey raastey par chal padta hai.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Imam Humaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Barqaani ne ''ya Rasulullah'' ke alfaz ke baad ''ما أضحک'', aap ko kis chiz ne hansaayaa'' ke alfaz ka izafa kiya hai."
6037,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(Mairaj ki raat) main jannat mein dakhil hua to maine Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya (biwi) Rumaisa ko dekha (neez) maine qadmon ki aawaz suni to maine poochha, ye kon hai? unhoney bataya : ye Bilal hain, maine eik mehal dekha, uskey sehan main eik londi dekhi , maine puchha : ''ye (mehal) kis ke liye hai? '' unhoney bataya, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye hai, maine uskey andar dakhil honey ka irada kiya ta ke main usey dekh sakun , lekin mujhey tumhari ghairat yad aa gaee.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey waliden aap par qurban hon, kya main aap se ghairat karunga. muttafaq aleh."
6038,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main so raha tha ke maine logon ko dekha ke wo merey samney pesh kiye gaey hain, un par qameesein thin, un mein se kisi ki qamis seeney tak pahunchti thi, kisi ki us se chhoti thi, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) mujh par pesh kiye gaey, un par jo qamis thi wo (chaltey waqt) usey ghaseet'tey they.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aapney uski kya taaweel farmaee hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(us sey) Deen murad hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6039,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''main soyaa hua tha to merey paas doodh ka piyala laya gaya to maine pi liya yahan tak ke sairaabi ka asar maine apney naakhunon mein zahir hota dekha, phir maine apney se bacha hua umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko ata kiya : ''Sahaba ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aapney iski kya taaweel farmaee? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ilm.'' muttafaq aleh."
6040,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''main so raha tha ke maine apney aap ko eik kunwen par dekha, is par eik dol tha, jis qadr Allah ne chaha maine us se pani nikala, phir ibne-Abi Qahaafa (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey hasil kar liya, unhoney eik ya do dol nikaley, aur unke nikalney mein zauf (kamzori) tha, Allah unke zauf (kamzori) ko maaf farmaey, phir wo (dol) badey dol mein badal gaya, aur umr bin Khattab ne usey pakad liya, maine aisa taqatwar aadmi nahin dekha jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah dol kheenchtaa ho, yahan tak ke logon ne apney oonton ko hoz se sairab kiya.'' muttafaq aleh."
6041,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir Abu-Bakar ke haath se ibne Khattab ne usey ley liya to wo unke haath mein bada ho gaya, maine aisa sardar nahin dekha jo unki tarah kaam karta ho, yahan tak ke log sairab ho gaey aur unhoney oonton ko bhi hoz se sairab kiya.'' muttafaq aleh."
6042,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne haq ko umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki zaban aur unke dil par jari farma diya hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6043,"Aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein jo ke Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, farmaya : ''Allah ne haq ko umr ki zaban par rakh diya hai jiskey zariey wo boltey hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
6044,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham is baat ko baeed (door) nahin samajhtey ke taskeen bakhshney wala kalam umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki zaban par jari hota hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa).
6045,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dua farmaee : aey Allah ! Islam ko Abu-Jahal bin Hisham ya umr bin Khattab ke zariey ghalba ata farma.'' subah hui to umr pehley pahar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, aur Islam qubul kiya, phir aapney masjid mein elania Namaz ada farmaee. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
6046,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : aey wo insan jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad sab se behtar shakhsiyat hai ! Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : sun lo ! agar aapney ye baat ki hai to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''Umar se behtar shakhs koi nahin jis par Suraj tulu hua ho.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6047,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar merey baad koi Nabi hota to wo umr bin Khattab hotey.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6048,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ghazwe ke liye tashrif ley gaey, jab aap wapis huey to eik siyah faam (rang) aurat aap ke paas aai to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine nazar maana thi ke agar Allah aap ko sahih salaamat wapis ley aaya to main aap ke samney daf bajaungi aur ghazl padhungi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''agar tu ney nazar maana thi to phir daf baja ley aur agar nazar nahin maana to phir nahin.'' wo bajaney lagi to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye, wo (unke aaney par) bajati rahi , phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye aur wo bajati rahi, phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to wo bajati rahi, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to usney daf apney peeth ke nichey rakh li aur is par beth gaee, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' umr ! shetan tum se darta hai, main betha hua tha aur wo daf bajati rahi, Abu-Bakar aaye to wo bajati rahi, phir Ali aaye to wo bajati rahi, phir Usman aaye to wo bajati rahi , umr jab tum aaye to usney daf phenk di.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6049,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they ke ham ne shor aur bachon ki aawaz suni, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey to dekha ke eik Habshi khatoon raqs kar rahi thi aur bachchey uskey ird-gird (tamasha dekh rahey) they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! aao aur dekho.'' main aai to maine apney chehra Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kandhey par rakh diya aur main aap ke kandhey aur sar ke darmiyan se usey dekhney lagi , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kya tum sair nahin hui, kya tum sair nahin hui? ''main kehney lagi nahin, taake main aap ke yahan apni qadr aur manzilat ka andaza laga sakoon, achcha umr (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaye to sarey log us (habshiya) ke paas se titar bitar ho gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine shayatin jin aur insanon ko dekha ke wo umr ki wajeh se bhag rahey hain.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : main wapis aa gaee. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6050,"Hazrat Anas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine teen umur (baton) mein apney rab se muwaafiqat ki, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar ham maqame Ibrahim ko jaey Namaz bana len? Allah ne ye aayat nazil farma di : ''maqame Ibrahim ko jaey Namaz banaao.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap ki paak biviyon ke paas nek aur fasiq qism ke log aatey hain, agar aap unhen parda karney ka hukm farma den, tab Allah ne aayat hijaab nazil farmaee, aur (eik moqe par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyan qissa ghairat (shehad peeney waley waqia) par ikhatti ho gaeen, to maine kaha : ''qarib hai ke uska rab , agar wo tumhen Talaq dey den, tum se behtar biwiyan unhen ata farma dey.'' isi tarah aayat nazil ho gaee. Bukhari."
6051,"Aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, unhoney kaha, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine teen umur (baton) mein , apney rab se muwaafiqat ki, maqame Ibrahim ke mutalliq, pardey aur Badr ke qaidiyon ke barey mein. muttafaq aleh."
6052,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko chaar chizon ki wajeh se deegar logon par fazilat ata ki gaee, unhoney Badr ke qaidiyon ko qatl karney ka mashwara diya tha, Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''agar Allah ki kitab mein ye hukm pehley se mojud na hota to tum ne jo (fidya) liya is par tumhen bada azab pahunchta.'' aur unka hijaab ke mutalliq farmana , unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyon se farmaya ke wo parda kiya karen, to Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen farmaya : ibne Khattab ! kya aap hamein hukm detey hain jabkey ""wahi"" to hamarey gharon mein utarti hai, tab Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : ''aur jab tum un se koi chiz talab karo to un se pardey ke peechey se talab karo.'' aur unke mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki dua : ''aey Allah ! umr ke zariey Islam ko taqwiyat farma.'' aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke (khalifa honey ke) mutalliq sab se pehli unhin ki raey thi aur unhoney hi sab se pehley unki baiat ki. rawahu Ahmed."
6053,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo aadmi meri ummat mein se jannat main eik darja buland maqam par faaiz hoga.'' Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! hamarey khayal mein wo aadmi umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) hi hain yahan tak ke wo wafat pa gaey. rawahu ibne-Maja."
6054,"Hazrat Aslam (Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam) bayan kartey hain, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke baaz halaat ke mutalliq puchha to maine unhen bataya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ke baad kisi shakhs ko itni ziyada jiddojehad aur sakhawat karney wala nahin dekha yahan tak ke ye fazaail umr (Raziallahu anhu) par khatam ho gaey. Bukhari."
6055,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi kar diye gaey to wo takleef mehsus karney lagey , is par ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen tasalli detey huey arz kiya : Ameerul Momineen ! aap itni takleef ka kyon izhar kar rahey hain? aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki aur usey achchhey andaz mein nibhaayaa , phir wo aap se juda huey to wo aap par razi they, phir aap Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat mein rahey, aur unke sath bhi khub rahey, phir wo aap se juda huey to wo bhi aap par razi they, phir aap musalmanon ki sohbat mein rahey, aur aap unke sath bhi khub achchhi tarah rahey, aur agar aap un se juda huey to aap un se bhi isi haal mein juda hongey ke wo aap se razi hongey, unhoney farmaya : tum ne jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath aur aap ke razi honey ka zikr kiya hai to wo Allah ki taraf se eik ehsan hai jo usney mujh par kiya hai, aur tum ne jo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath aur unke razi honey ka zikr kiya hai to wo bhi Allah ki taraf se eik ehsan hai jo usney mujh par kiya hai, aur rahi meri ghabrahat aur pareshani jo tum dekh rahey ho to wo aap aur aap ke sathiyon ke barey mein fikr mand honey ki wajeh se hai, Allah ki qism ! agar merey paas zamin bhar sona hota to main Allah ke azab ko dekhney se pehley uska fidya de-kar us se najat hasil karta. Bukhari."
6056,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is beech mein ke eik aadmi gaaey haank raha tha, jab wo thak jata to wo is par Sawar ho jata, usney kaha : hamein isliye nahin paida kiya gaya, hamein to khet jotne ke liye paida kiya gaya hai, logon ne kaha : Subhanallah : gaaey kalam karti hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main is par eman rakhta hun Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi is par eman rakhtey hain.'' aur wo dono us waqt wahan mojud nahin they, aur farmaya : ''eik aadmi bakriyan charaa raha tha ke bhediye ne eik bakri par hamla kiya aur usey pakad liya , uskey Malik ne usey ja liya aur usey chuda liya , bhediye ne usey kaha : jis din darindey hi darindey reh jaeyngey aur us din merey siwa bakriyon ko charaney wala kon hoga? logon ne kaha : Subhanallah ! bhediya kalam karta hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main is par eman rakhta hun aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) is par eman rakhtey hain.'' aur wo dono us waqt wahan mojud nahin they. muttafaq aleh."
6057,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main un logon mein khada tha jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye duayen kar rahey they, aur unka janaza unki chaar pai par rakha hua tha, ke achcha eik aadmi ne merey peechhey se apni kohni merey kandhon par rakh di, aur wo keh rahey they : Allah aap (Raziallahu anhu) par rehem farmaai , mujhey ummid hai ke Allah aap ko aap ke dono sathiyon ke sath (dafn) karaaega. kyonkey main aksar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna karta tha : ''main, Abu-Bakar aur umr they, main, Abu-Bakar aur umr ne kalam kiya, main, Abu-Bakar aur umr gaey, main, Abu-Bakar aur umr dakhil huye, main, Abu-Bakar aur umr bahar nikley.'' maine jo mud kar dekha to wo Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) they. muttafaq aleh."
6058,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat waley maqame-illiyeen walon ko is tarah dekhengey jis tarah tum aasman ke ufuq mein chamak daar sitarey ko dekhtey ho, aur Abu-Bakar aur umr unhi mein se hain, aur wo kya khub hain.'' Sharahus-sunnah , Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja ne isi tarah riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah, Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja)."
6059,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ehle jannat ke awwaleen aur aakhareen ke umr raseeda logon ke sardar hongey albatta Anbiya (Alaihissalam) aur Rasool us se mustashnaa (alag) hongey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6060,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja.
6061,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main nahin janta ke main tum mein kitni der baqi rahunga , merey baad tum Abu-Bakar aur umr dono ki iqtida (pairvi) karna.'' raah Tirmizi."
6062,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab masjid mein tashrif latey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa koi apna sar na uthata wo dono aap ki taraf dekh kar muskuraatey aur aap un dono ki taraf dekh kar muskuraatey they. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6063,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey) bahar nikley aur masjid mein dakhil huey. aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) mein se eik aap ke daain taraf tha aur eik aap ke baain taraf tha, aap un dono ke haath pakdey huey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat ham isi tarah uthaey jaeyngey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6064,Hazrat Abdullah bin Hantab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to farmaya : ''ye dono samaa (sunnewale) aur basar (dekhnewale) (ki tarah) hain.'' Imam Tirmizi ne isey mursal riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
6065,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ke aasman walon se do wazir hain aur zamin walon se do wazir hain. aasman walon se merey do wazir Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aur mekael (Alaihissalam) hain, aur zamin walon mein se Abu-Bakar aur umr hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6066,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, maine (khuwab mein) dekha ke goya eik tarazu aasman se utra hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se wazan kiya gaya to aap bhari rahey, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka wazan kiya gaya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhari rahey, umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka wazan kiya gaya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhari rahey, phir tarazu utha li gaee. us se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghamgin huye, yani us (khuwab) ne aap ko ghamgin kar diya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nabuwat ka khilaafat ki janib ishara hai, phir Allah jisey chahega badshahat ata farmaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
6067,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ehle jannat mein se eik aadmi tumharey paas zahir hoga.'' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ehle jannat mein se eik aadmi tumharey paas zahir hoga.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6068,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain chaandni raat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sar Mubarak meri god mein tha ke achcha maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya kisi shakhs ki aasman ke sitaron ke barabar nekiyan hongi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, Umar.'' maine arz kiya, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki nekiyan kahan gaeen? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umar ki sari nekiyan, Abu-Bakar ki nekiyon ke muqabley main eik neki ki manind hain.'' rawahu rizeen."
6069,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghar mein letey huey they aur us waqt aap ki raanon ya pindliyon se kapda utha hua tha, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki to unhen ijazat de-di gaee aur aap usi haalat mein rahey, unhoney baat cheet ki, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki to aapney unhen ijazat de-di aur aap usi haalat mein rahey, unhoney baat cheet ki, phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth kar beth gaey, apney kapdey durust kiye , jab wo (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se uth kar) chaley gaey to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kiya, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to aapney unki khatir koi harkat na ki aur na unki koi parwah ki, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to aapney unki khatir koi harkat ki na unki koi parwah ki, phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to aap uth kar beth gaey aur apney kapdey durust kiye , (kya maamla hai?) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main us shakhs se haya na karun jis se farishtey haya kartey hain?'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aapney farmaya : ''Usman haya daar shakhs hai, mujhey andesha hua ke agar maine unhen isi haalat mein andar aaney ki ijazat de-di to ho sakta hai ke (sharam ke maarey) wo apney kisi kaam ke barey main apni baat mujhey na pahuncha saken.'' rawahu Muslim."
6070,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ka eik rafeeq (khas) hota hai aur merey rafeeq yani jannat mein, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6071,"Aur ibne-Maja ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, aur Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur iski sanad qawi nahin, aur wo munqata' hai. rawahu ibne-Maja."
6072,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein us waqt hazir hua jab aap ghazwae-tabuk ke liye aamada kar rahey they, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! so oont ma' saazo saman Allah ki raah mein merey zimmey hain, phir aapney lashkar ke liye aamada kiya to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kiya, Allah ki raah mein do sau oont ma' saazo saman merey zimmey hain, phir aapney targheeb dilai to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey to arz kiya, Allah ki raah mein teen sau oont merey zimmey hain. raawi bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member se utartey farma rahey they : ''Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey baad jo bhi amal kiya is par koi muwaakhiza (pakad) nahin, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) uskey baad jo bhi amal karey is par koi muwaakhiza nahin. rawahu Tirmizi."
6073,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jaish usraa tayyar farmaya to Usman ne apni jeib main eik hazar Dinar la kar aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiye aur aap ki god mein dher kar diye , maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apni god mein unhen palat rahey they aur farma rahey they : ''Usman ne jo bhi amal kiya aaj ke baad wo uskey liye nuqsan deh nahin.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do martaba aisey farmaya. rawahu Ahmed."
6074,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baiate-rizwaan ke liye hukm farmaya to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Makka ki taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qaasid bin kar gaey they, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne baiat ki, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Usman Allah aur uskey Rasool ke kaam se gaey huey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna eik haath doosrey par maara, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khatir unke apni zaat ki khatir haathon se behtar tha. rawahu Tirmizi."
6075,"Hazrat Samama bin Huzn Qusheiri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main us waqt ghar ke paas tha, jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apney ghar sey) jhank kar farmaya : main tumhen Allah aur Islam ka wasta de-kar poochhta hun, kya tum jantey ho ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madiney tashrif laye to ruma kunwen ke ilawa wahan mitha pani nahin tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ruma-kunwen ko kharid kar musalmanon ke liye waqf kar dega to uskey liye jannat mein us se behtar hoga.'' maine apney khalis maal se usey kharid , aur aaj tum mujhey uska pani peeney se rok rahey ho yahan tak ke main samandari pani pi raha hun, unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! aisey hi hai, phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main tumhen Allah aur Islam ka wasta de-kar poochhta hun : kya tum jantey ho ke masjid apney namaaziyon ke liye tang thi, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs aale falan se zamin ka qat'aa (hissa) kharid kar us se masjid ko badha dega to uskey liye jannat mein us se behtar hoga.'' maine apney khalis maal se usey kharid , aur aaj tum mujhey is mein do rakaat Namaz ada karney se rok rahey ho, unhoney kaha : haan ! aisey hi hai, aapney farmaya : main Allah aur Islam ka wasta de-kar tumhen poochhta hun, kya tum jantey ho ke jaishul-usra ko maine apney maal se tayyar kiya tha? unhoney kaha : haan ! Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main Allah aur Islam ka wasta de-kar tum se poochhta hun : kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka ke pahad par they, aur us waqt Abu-Bakar, umr aur main aap ke sath they, pahad ne harkat ki yahan tak ke zamin par kuchh tukdey gir gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney paaon se usey thokar maar kar farmaya : ''pahad thehar ja, tujh par eik Nabi hai, eik Siddiq hai aur do Shahid hain?'' unhoney kaha : haan ! aisey hi hai, aapney teen baar farmaya : Allahu-Akbar ! rab Kaba ki qism ! unhoney gawahi de-di ke main Shahid hun. rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai aur Dar-Qutni."
6076,"Hazrat Murra bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aapney fitnon ka zikr kiya aur unke qarib honey ka irshad farmaya , itney main eik aadmi guzra, usney eik kapda lapet rakha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya ye shakhs us (fitney ke) din hidayat par hoga.'' main unki taraf gaya, dekha ke wo Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) hain. raawi bayan kartey hain, maine unka chehra aap ki taraf pher kar arz kiya : ye wo (aadmi) hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
6077,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Usman ! ummid hai ke Allah tumhen qamis pahnaaega , agar wo tum se usey utarwana chahen to tum unki khatir usey na utaarnaa.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : hadees mein taweel qissa hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
6078,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik fitney ka zikr kiya to farmaya : ''ye yani Usman is mein mazloom Shahid kar diye jaeyngey.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai iski sanad gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6079,"Hazrat Abu-Sahla (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne muhaasrey ke din mujhey farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se eik ehad liya tha aur is par main qaaim hun.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6080,"Hazrat Usman bin Abdullah bin Mohab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ehle Misr se eik aadmi Haj ke iraday se aaya to usney kuchh logon ko bethey huey dekh kar kaha : ye kon log hain? unhoney bataya : ye Quraishi hain, usney kaha : un mein Shaikh (moatabar aalim) kon hai? unhoney kaha : Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu), us aadmi ne kaha : ibne-Umar ! main tum se kisi chiz ke mutalliq sawal karta hun, mujhey bataeyn , kya aap jantey hain ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ghazwae uhad mein farar ho gaey they? unhoney farmaya : haan, usney kaha kya aap jantey hain ke wo ghazwae Badr mein bhi shareek nahin huey they? unhoney farmaya : haan , usney kaha : kya aap jantey hain ke baiate-rizwaan ke moqe par bhi wo mojud nahin they? unhoney farmaya : haan , usney kaha : Allahu-Akbar : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aao main tumhen wazeh karta hun, raha unka ghazwae uhad se farar hona to main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ne unhen maaf farma diya hai, raha unka Badr se ghayeb hona to uski wajeh ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Ruqayya (Raziallahu anhu) unki ehliya (biwi) thin aur wo bimar thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''aap ke liye ghazwae-Badr mein shareek honey waley Mujahid ke barabar ajr aur sawab hai aur uskey barabar aap ke liye maale-ghanimat mein se hissey bhi hai.'' raha unka baiate-rizwaan ke waqt mojud na hona, to agar Makka mein Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se ziyada koi moazziz hota to aap usey bhejtey, lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja , aur baiate-rizwaan Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke Makka chaley janey ke baad hui thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney daain haath ke mutalliq farmaya : ''ye Usman ka haath hai.'' aur usey apney haath par maara aur farmaya : ''ye Usman ke liye hai.'' phir ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ab ye (jawabat) apney sath ley jana (aur inhen yad rakhna). Bukhari."
6081,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam Abu-Sahla bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se makhfi (chhipe) taur par koi baat kar rahey they, aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka rang mutghaiyar (badal) ho raha tha, jab muhaasrey ka din tha to ham ne kaha : kya ham ladaai nahin karengey? unhoney farmaya : nahin, kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey eik Amr (baat) ki wasiyat ki hai aur main apney aap ko uska paband rakhunga. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun-nubuwa)."
6082,"Hazrat abu Habiba se riwayat hai ke wo ghar mein dakhil huey jabkey Usman is mein mahsoor (band) they, aur unhoney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna ke wo Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se baat karney ki ijazat talab kar rahey hain, unhen ijazat mil gaee , wo khadey huey Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''merey baad tum fitna aur ikhtilaf dekhogey.'' ya farmaya : ''ikhtilaf aur fitna dekhogey.'' kisi ne aap se arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey liye kya hukm hai ya aap hamein kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ameer aur uskey sathiyon ko lazim pakdo.'' aur aap us (Ameer) ke mutalliq Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf ishara farma rahey they. Imam Behaqi ne dono hadisen dalaeelun-nubuwa mein riwayat ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun-nubuwa)."
6083,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uhad pahad par chadhey , Abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath they, usney harkat ki to aapney is par apna paaon maar kar farmaya : ''Uhad ! thehar jaao , tum par eik Nabi hai, eik Siddiq aur do Shahid hain.'' Bukhari."
6084,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Madina ke eik baagh mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha, eik aadmi aaya aur usney darwaza kholney ki darkhast ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey liye darwaza khol do , aur usey jannat ki basharat do.'' chunanche maine us shakhs ke liye darwaza khol diya to wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq unhen jannat ki basharat sunai to unhoney Allah ki hamd bayan ki, phir eik aur aadmi aaya aur usney bhi darwaza kholney ka kaha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey liye bhi darwaza khol do , aur usey bhi jannat ki basharat sunaao.'' chunanche maine uskey liye darwaza khola to wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) they, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq unhen bhi jannat ki basharat sunai to unhoney Allah ki hamd bayan ki, phir eik aur aadmi ne darwaza kholney ki darkhast ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''uskey liye darwaza khol do aur usey bhi jannat ki basharat suna do, un masaayib (musibaton) ke baad jin sey unka wasta padega.'' to wo Usman (Raziallahu anhu) they, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq unhen bataya to unhoney Allah ki hamd bayan ki . phir farmaya : Allah hi se madad darkar hai. muttafaq aleh."
6085,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hayaat mubaraka mein Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
6086,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''raat mujhey khuwab main eik mard Saleh dikhaya gaya goya wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain, jo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath muallaq hain, umr Abu-Bakar ke sath muallaq hain, aur Usman umr ke sath muallaq hain.'' Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se uthey to ham ne kaha : mard Saleh se murad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain, aur doosrey jo eik doosrey ke sath latkey huey hain, us se murad ye hai ke wo is Deen ke wali hain, jiskey sath Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Nabi banakar bheja hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
6087,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''aap merey liye aisey hain jaisey Musa (Alaihissalam) ke liye Harun (Alaihissalam) they, albatta merey baad koi Nabi nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
6088,"Hazrat Zar bin Habish bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jisney daney ko ugaya aur her zi rooh ko paida farmaya ! Nabi ummi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey ehad diya ke momin shakhs hi mujh se mohabbat kerega aur sirf munafiq shakhs hi mujh se dushmani rakhega. rawahu Muslim."
6089,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-khaibar ke moqe par farmaya : ''main kal eik aisey shakhs ko parcham ata karunga jiskey haathon Allah Fateh ata farmaeyga, wo shakhs Allah aur Rasool se mohabbat karta hai, aur Allah aur uska Rasool usey mehbub rakhtey hain.'' chunanche jab subh hui to tamam log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, aur wo sab pur-ummeed they ke wo (parcham) usey ata kiya jaeyga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ali bin Abi Talib kahan hain?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! unki aakhon mein takleef hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen bulaao.'' wo aap ke paas laye gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki aakhon mein apna luaab lagaya to wo aisey shifaayaab huey ke goya unhen koi takleef thi hi nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne parcham unhen ata farmaya to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya main un se ladtaa rahun yahan tak ke wo hamarey jaisey (yani musalman) ho jaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yunhi chaltey raho yahan tak ke tum unke maidan mein utro, phir unhen Islam ki dawat pesh karo aur unhen bataao ke Allah ke kya huquq un par wajib hain, Allah ki qism ! agar tumharey zariey Allah kisi eik aadmi ko hidayat ata farma dey to wo tumharey liye surkh oonton se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''tu mujh se aur main tum se hun, (باب بلوغ الصغیر) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
6090,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ali mujh se hain aur main un se hun aur wo her momin ke dost hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
6091,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main jis ka dost hun, Ali uskey dost hain.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
6092,"Hazrat Hubshi bin Junaada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ali mujh se hain aur main un se hun, aur meri taraf se koi adaegi na karey siwaye merey aur Ali ke.'' Tirmizi, aur Imam Ahmed ne isey Abu-Janawa se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Ahmed."
6093,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba ke darmiyan bhai chaara qaaim kiya to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aakhon mein aansu ke sath aaye aur arz kiya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmiyan bhai chaara qaaim kiya hai, lekin aapney merey aur kisi aur ke darmiyan bhai chaara qaaim nahin farmaya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum merey duniya aur aakhirat mein bhai ho.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6094,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik bhuna hua perinda tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! apni makhluq mein se apney mehbub tareen shakhs ko merey paas bhej jo merey sath is perindey ko khaye.'' Ali (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas tashrif laye aur unhoney aap ke sath khaya (khaaya). Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6095,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se koi chiz talab karta to aap mujhey ata farmatey aur jab main khamosh rehta to aap talab kiye baghair mujhey ata farma detey they. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6096,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main daare-hikmat (hikmat ka shehar) hun aur Ali uska darwaza hain.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye hadees gharib hai, aur unhoney farmaya : baaz raawiyon ne is hadees ko Shareek se riwayat kiya hai, aur unhoney is mein an As Sunabihi ka zikr nahin kiya, aur ham Shareek ke ilawa ye hadees kisi bharosemand raawi se nahin jantey. rawahu Tirmizi."
6097,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Taaif ke roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur un se sargoshi farmaee. logon ne kaha : aap ki apney chacha zaad ke sath sargoshi taweel (lambi) ho gaee , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine us se sargoshi nahin ki, balke Allah ne us se sargoshi ki hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6098,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Ali ! merey aur tumharey siwa kisi ke liye durust nahin ke wo haalate-janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan hambistari ke baad ki napaaki ki haalat) mein us masjid mein se guzrey.'' Ali bin munzir bayan kartey hain, maine Zaraar bin Surad se puchha : is hadees ka kya maana hai? unhoney farmaya : merey aur terey siwa kisi ke liye durust nahin ke wo haalate-janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan hambistari ke baad ki napaaki ki haalat) mein masjid se raastey ka kaam ley. Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6099,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik lashkar rawana kiya, is mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney haath utha kar dua kartey huey suna : ''aey Allah ! mujhey maut na dena yahan tak ke to mujhey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dikha dey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6100,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''munafiq shakhs Ali se mohabbat kerega na momin shakhs un se dushmani rakhega.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees sanad ke lihaz se Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
6101,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Ali ko bura bhala kaha to usney mujhey bura bhala kaha.'' rawahu Ahmed."
6102,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein Esa (Alaihissalam) ki eik mushaabihat hai, Yahudi un se dushmani rakhtey hain, yahan tak ke wo unki walida (mutahra) par tohmat lagatey hain jabkey Nasara un se mohabbat kartey hain, yahan tak ke unhoney unhen aisey maqam par faaiz kar (virajmaan) diya jiskey wo haq daar nahin.'' phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : do qism ke log merey (haq ke) mutalliq halak ho jaeyngey, muhabbat mein had se badh jaanewala.wo merey mutalliq aisi baaton mein had se badh jaega jo mujh mein nahin hai, aur dushmani rakhney wala ki meri dushmani usey is par aamada karegi ke wo mujh par bohtan lagaega. rawahu Ahmed."
6103,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib aur Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab Ghadeer kham par padaaw dala to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka haath pakad kar farmaya : ''kya tum nahin jantey ke mera mominon par unki janon se bhi ziyada haq hai?'' unhoney kaha : kyon nahin ! zarur hai, phir farmaya : ''kya tum nahin jantey ke mera her momin par uski jaan se bhi ziyada haq hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, kyon nahin ! zarur hai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! main jis shakhs ka dost hun Ali uskey dost hain, aey Allah ! jo shakhs usko dost banaey to usey dost bana, aur jo shakhs is se dushmani rakhey to unhen dushman bana.'' uskey baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) Ali se miley to unhoney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ibne-Abi Talib ! aap ko Mubarak ho aap subah aur Sham (her waqt) her momin aur her momina ke dost bin gaey. rawahu Ahmed."
6104,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) se shaadi ka pegham bheja to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo to chhoti (kam-sin) hain.'' phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen pegham bheja to aapney unki shaadi un se kar di. rawahu Nasai."
6105,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baab Ali ke siwa tamam darwazey band karney ka hukm farmaya. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6106,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan jo mera maqam aur martaba tha wo makhluq mein se kisi aur ka nahin tha, main sehri ke awwal waqt (raat ke aakhiri chhatey hissey) main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aata to main kehta, Allah ke Nabi ! aap par salamti ho, agar aap khans detey to main ehle khana ke paas wapis chala jata, warna main aap ke yahan dakhil ho jata. rawahu Nasai."
6107,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main mareez tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey , aur us waqt main keh raha tha, aey Allah ! agar meri maut ka waqt aa chuka hai to mujhey (maut ke zariey) rahat ata farma , aur agar abhi der hai to phir mujhey sehat ata farma , aur agar ye aazmaaish hai to phir mujhey sabr ata farma, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kaisey kaha hai?'' maine aap ko dobara suna diya, aapney usey apna paaon maara aur farmaya : ''aey Allah ! inhen aafiyat ata farma.'' ya farmaya : ''isey shifa ata farma.'' raawi ko is mein shak hua hai, wo bayan kartey hain, iskey baad mujhey takleef nahin hui. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6108,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, un hazraat sey, jin par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) martey dam tak khush rahey, is Amr khilaafat ka koi shakhs haq daar nahin, unhoney naam ginwaaey , Ali , Usman , Zuber , Talha , Saad aur Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu). Bukhari."
6109,"Hazrat Qais bin Abi Hazim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka haath shal (be-harkat) dekha jiskey sath unhoney ghazwae uhad mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (dushman ke waar sey) bachaya tha. Bukhari."
6110,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-ehzaab ke roz farmaya : ''kon shakhs merey paas lashkar ki khabar layega?'' Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : main ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ka eik hawaari (mukhlis mazdoor) hota hai aur merey hawaari Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
6111,"Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kon shakhs banu Qureza jaey aur unke mutalliq khabar merey paas laye? ''main gaya, aur jab main wapis aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey liye farmaya : ''tujh par merey waliden fidaa hon.'' muttafaq aleh."
6112,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke ilawa kisi aur shakhs ke liye apney waliden ko eik sath jama kartey (yani merey maa baap tujh par fidaa hon) nahin suna, kyonkey ghazwae uhad ke moqe par maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Saad ! teer andazi karo, merey waliden tum par qurban hon.'' muttafaq aleh."
6113,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah ki raah mein teer chalaney wala main pehla Arbi shakhs hun. muttafaq aleh."
6114,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (kisi ghazwe se wapis) Madina aaye to raat bhar jaagtey rahey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kash koi mard Saleh merey liye pehra deta, itney mein ham ne hathiyaron ki aawaz (jhankaar) suni , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : main Saad hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aap yahan kaisey aaye?'' unhoney arz kiya : merey dil mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq khof sa paida hua to main aap ke liye pehra deney aaya hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmaee phir so gaey. muttafaq aleh."
6115,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her ummat ke liye eik ameen hota hai aur is ummat ke ameen Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
6116,"Hazrat ibne-Abi Muleka (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se us waqt suna jab un se ye sawal kiya gaya ke agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ko khalifa naamzad kartey to aap kisey naamzad farmatey? unhoney farmaya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu), puchha gaya : phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad kon? unhoney farmaya : umr (Raziallahu anhu), puchha gaya : umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad kon? unhoney farmaya : Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu). rawahu Muslim."
6117,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abu-Bakar, umr , Usman , Ali , Talha aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) hirra par they ke pathar ne harkat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' thehar ja , tujh par Nabi , Siddiq aur Shahid hain.'' aur baaz raawiyon ne Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ka izafa naqal kiya hai aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahin kiya. rawahu Muslim."
6118,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar jannat mein , umr jannat mein , Usman jannat mein , Ali jannat mein , Talha jannat mein , Zuber jannat mein , Abdur-Rehman bin Auf jannat mein , Saad bin Abi Waqas jannat mein , Saeed bin Zaid jannat mein aur Abu-Ubaida (Aamir) bin Jarrah jannat mein hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6119,Hazrat ibne-Maja (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja.
6120,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se meri ummat par sab se ziyada meharban Abu-Bakar hain, Allah ke Deen ke mamley mein sab se ziyada sakht umr hain, un mein se sab se ziyada ba haya Usman hain, ilm meeras ke sab se badey aalim Zaid bin Sabit hain, sab se badey qaari Ubai bin Kab hain, halal aur haram ke mutalliq sab se ziyada ilm rakhney waley Muaz bin Jabal hain, aur her ummat ka eik ameen hota hai aur is ummat ke ameen Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah hain.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi. aur Maamer se Qatada ki sanad se mursal riwayat hai, aur is mein hai : qaza mein sab se ziyada aalim Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain.''"
6121,"Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae-uhad ke moqe par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do zirhen pahni hui thin, aap eik chattan ki taraf mutawajjeh huey lekin aap is par chadh na sakey to Talha (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke nichey beth gaey yahan tak ke aap us chattan par pahunch gaey, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Talha ne (jannat ko) wajib kar liya.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6122,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf dekha to farmaya : ''jo shakhs ye pasand karta ho ke wo roey zamin par chaltey huey aisey shakhs ko dekhey jo apna ehad nibhaa chuka to wo is shakhs ko dekh ley.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs roey zamin par chaltey phirtey Shahid ko dekhna chahey to wo Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekh ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6123,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, merey kanon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Talha aur Zuber jannat mein merey hamsaaey hain.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6124,Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-uahad ke moqe par farmaya : ''aey Allah ! us (Saad (Raziallahu anhu)) ko teer andazi mein qawi bana aur uski dua qubul farma.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah).
6125,Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Saad jab tujh se dua karey to to uski dua qubul farma.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
6126,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sirf Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye apney waliden ko (fidaa honey par) ikhatta zikr kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae uhad ke moqe par unhen farmaya : ''merey maa baap tujh par fidaa hon teer andazi karo.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''qawi nojawan ! teer phenko.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6127,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saad (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye merey mamu hain, koi mujhey in jaisa apna mamu dikhaye.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bano zohra qabiley se they, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki walida mohtarma bhi bano zohra qabiley se thin, isi liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye merey mamu hain.'' aur masaabeh mein) فَلْیُرِنِیْ (ke bajaey : ( فَلْیُکْرِمَنَّ (ke alfaz hain. rawahu Tirmizi."
6128,"Hazrat Qais bin Abi Hazim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huey suna : main Arab mein sab se pehla shakhs hun jisney Allah ki raah mein teer andazi ki, aur hamari ye haalat thi ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad mein shareek hotey they aur hamara khana keekar ka phal aur keekar ke pattey hotey they, aur ham mein se her shakhs bakri ki tarah ijaabat (mighniyan) kiya karta tha wo (khushk honey ki wajeh sey) eik dusri ke sath judi hui nahin hoti thin, phir ye waqt aaya ke banu-Asad merey Islam ke mutalliq mujh par nukta chaini kartey hain, agar aisey ho to main na-murad hua aur merey amal barbad ho gaey, aur wo (banu Asad) un (Saad (Raziallahu anhu)) ke mutalliq umr (Raziallahu anhu) se shikayat kiya kartey they aur wo ye ke wo achhi tarah Namaz nahin padhtey they. muttafaq aleh."
6129,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main janta hun ke Islam qubul karney wala main teesra shakhs hun, jis din maine Islam qubul kiya usi roz doosrey bhi Islam mein dakhil huye, aur main saat din tak usi haalat mein raha ke main Islam qubul karney wala teesra shakhs hun. Bukhari."
6130,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni paak biviyon se farmaya kartey they : ''main apney baad tumharey barey mein bahut fikr mand hun, sabr karney waley aur siddiqeen hi un mushkil maamlat main tumhara sath dengey.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : yani sadqa karney waley, phir Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : Allah tumharey walid ko jannat ke chashmey salsabeel se pilaey , aur ibne-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne ummahaatul-momineen ke liye eik baagh waqf kiya tha jo chaalis hazar mein farokht kiya gaya tha. rawahu Tirmizi."
6131,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apni paak biviyon se farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs merey baad tum par kharch kerega to wo shakhs sacha aur ehsan karney wala hai, aey Allah ! Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ko jannat ke chashmey salsabeel se jaam pila.'' rawahu Ahmed."
6132,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Najran waley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kisi ameen shakhs ko hamari taraf mab-us farmana (bhejen), aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhari taraf aisey ameen shakhs ko bhejunga jo ke haqeeqi maana mein ameen hoga.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) us (amaarat) ke khahish mand they, raawi bayan kartey hain, aapney Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah ko bheja . muttafaq aleh."
6133,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham aap ke baad kisey khalifa muqarrar farmaeyn? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum Abu-Bakar ko ameer bana lo to tum unhen ameen , duniya se be raghbati rakhney wala aur aakhirat se raghbat rakhney wala paaogey . aur agar tum umr ko ameer muqarrar karogey to tum unhen qawi ameen paaogey, wo Allah ke mamley mein kisi malamat karney waley ki malamat se khof-zada nahin hotey. aur agar tum Ali ko ameer banaogey, halanke main nahin samajhta ke tum unhen banaogey, to tum unhen haadi aur hidayat yafta paaogey, wo tumhen siraate-mustaqeem par chalaengey.'' rawahu Ahmed."
6134,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah Abu-Bakar par rehem farmaai , unhoney apni beti se meri shaadi ki, daare-hijrat ki taraf mujhey utha kar (apney oont par Sawar karkey) ley gaey, ghaar mein merey sath rahey, aur apney maal se Bilal ko azad karaya. aur umr par rehem farmaai , wo haq farmatey hain chahey (chhahe) wo kadwa ho, haq goi ne unhen tanha chhod diya isliye unka koi dost nahin, Allah Usman par rehem farmaai , farishtey bhi un se haya kartey hain, Allah Ali par rehem farmaai , aey Allah ! wo jahan bhi jaeyn haq unke sath hi rahey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6135,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat (نَدْعُ اَبْنَاءَ نَا وَ اَبْنَاءَ کُمْ) nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali, Fatima, Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur farmaya : ''aey Allah ! ye merey ehle bait hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
6136,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, subah ke waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley us waqt aap par kaley baalon se bani hui naqsh-daar chadar thi, us doran Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to aapney unhen apney sath us (chadar) mein dakhil farma liya , phir Husain (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to aapney unhen bhi dakhil farma liya , phir Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) aayen to aapney unhen bhi dakhil farma liya , phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to aapney unhen bhi dakhil farma liya , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''Allah sirf yehi chahta hai, aey ehle bait ! ke wo tum se gunah ki gandagi door farma dey aur tumhen mukammal taur par paak saaf kar dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
6137,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke lakhte-jigar Ibrahim faut huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unke liye jannat main eik doodh pilaney wali hai.'' Bukhari."
6138,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyan (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki khidmat mein hazir thin, Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) aayin , wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunch gaeen , jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen dekha to farmaya : ''piyari beti ! khush aamadeed.'' phir aapney unhen bitha liya , phir un se sargoshi farmaee to wo bahut ziyada roney lagin , jab aapney unka gham dekha to aapney dusri martaba un se sargoshi farmaee wo hans den, chunanche jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey to maine Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tumharey sath kya sargoshi farmaee? unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke raz ko afshaan (faash) nahin karungi, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wafat pa gaey to maine kaha : mera aap par jo haq hai us hawaley se main aap ko qism de-kar poochhti hun kya aap mujhey nahin bataengi? unhoney farmaya : haan ! ab theek hai, jahan tak us pehli sargoshi ka talluq hai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bataya ke ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) her saal mujh se eik martaba Quran ka door kiya kartey they jabkey is saal unhoney do martaba door kiya hai, aur main samajhta hun ke waqt pura ho chuka hai, tum Allah se darti rehna aur sabr karna , aur main tumharey liye behtareen kaarwaan hun.'' lekin jab aapney meri ghabrahat dekhi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dusri martaba sargoshi ki aur farmaya : ''Fatima ! kya tum is par khush nahin ke tum ehle jannat ki khawatin ya mominon ki khawatin ki sardar hongi?'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se sargoshi ki to mujhey bataya ke isi takleef mein unki rooh qabz ki jaeygi to is par main ro padi , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se sargoshi ki to mujhey bataya ke aap ke ehle bait mein se sab se pehley main aap ke peechey aaungi, to is par main hans padi. muttafaq aleh."
6139,Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Fatima merey jigar ka tukda hai jisney us se dushmani rakhi usney mujh se dushmani rakhi.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jo chiz usey baichaini mein mubtala kar deti hai wohi chiz mujhey baichaini mein mubtala kar deti hai aur jo chiz usey eza (takleef) pahunchati hai wohi chiz mujhey eza (takleef) pahunchati hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
6140,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Makka aur Madina ke darmiyan pani ki jagah par kham naami maqam par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khutba irshad farmaya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, waaz aur nasihat ki phir farmaya : ''امابعد ! logo ! suno ! main bhi insan hun, qarib hai ke merey rab ka qaasid aaye aur main uski baat qubul kar lun , main tum mein do azeem chizen chhod kar ja raha hun, un dono mein se pehli chiz Allah ki kitab hai, is mein hidayat aur Noor hai, tum Allah ki kitab ko pakdo aur us se tamassuk (mazboot talluq) ikhtiyar karo.'' aapney Allah ki kitab (par amal karney) par ubhaaraa aur uskey mutalliq targheeb dilai, phir farmaya : ''(doosri chiz) merey ehle-bait, main apney ehle bait ke mutalliq tumhen Allah se darata hun, apney ehle bait ke mutalliq main tumhen Allah se darata hun.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ki kitab , wo Allah ki rassi hai, jisney uski ittiba ki wo hidayat par hai, aur jisney usey chhod diya wo gumrahi par hoga.'' rawahu Muslim."
6141,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab wo ibne Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ko salam kiya kartey they to yun kehtey they : Jul-Janaahain (Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ka laqab) ke bete ! tum par salam ho. Bukhari.
6142,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha us waqt Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke kandhey par they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''aey Allah ! main is se mohabbat karta hon to bhi is se mohabbat farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
6143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, din ke kisi hissey mein main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana hua yahan tak ke aap Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar tashrif ley gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''kya yahan chhota bachcha hai kya yahan chhota bachcha yani Hasan hai?'' thodi der guzri thi ke wo daudtey huey aaye yahan tak ke un dono mein se her eik ne apney sathi ko galey lagaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! be-shak main is se mohabbat karta hun, to bhi is se mohabbat rakhney waley se mohabbat farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
6144,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par dekha jabkey Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke pehlu mein they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik martaba logon ki taraf tawajjoh farmatey aur dusri martaba un Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tawajjoh farmatey, aur farmatey : ''be-shak mera ye beta sardar hai, ummid hai ke Allah uski wajeh se musalmanon ki do azeem jamaaton ke darmiyan suleh karaaega.'' Bukhari."
6145,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Nuaim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se us waqt suna jab un se kisi aadmi ne mohrim (haalate ehram waley shakhs) ke mutalliq masla daryaft kiya, Shoba bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai ke wo poochh raha tha (agar-mohrim) makkhi maar dey (to is par kya kaffara hoga?) unhoney farmaya : ehle Iraq makkhi (maarney) ke mutalliq mujh se masla daryaft kartey hain jabkey unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke nawaasey ko qatl kar diya, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ''wo dono (Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) duniya mein merey do phool hain.'' Bukhari."
6146,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sab se ziyada mushaabihat rakhtey they. aur unhoney Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein bhi farmaya : wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se un sab se ziyada mushaabihat rakhtey they. Bukhari."
6147,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey seeney se laga kar farmaya : ''aey Allah ! isey hikmat ki taalim ata farma.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''isey kitab ki taalim ata farma.'' Bukhari."
6148,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) mein dakhil huey to maine tahaarat ke liye pani rakh diya, chunanche jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye to farmaya : ''ye kis ne rakha tha?'' aap ko bataya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! isey Deen ki samajh boojh ata farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
6149,Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap mujhey aur Hasan ko pakad kar farmatey : ''aey Allah ! in se mohabbat farma kyonkey main in dono se mohabbat karta hun.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey pakad kar apni eik raan par bitha letey they aur Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni dusri raan par bitha letey phir unhen mila kar farmatey : ''aey Allah ! in dono par rehem farma kyonkey main un par shafqat aur rehmat farmata hun.'' Bukhari.
6150,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik lashkar bheja to is par Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko Ameer muqarrar farmaya , kuchh logon ne unki amaarat ke barey mein aetraz kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum uski amaarat par aetraz kartey ho to tum is se pehley uskey walid ki amaarat ke barey mein bhi aetraz kar chukey ho. Allah ki qism ! bila-shuba wo amaarat ke ziyada laaiq tha aur wo tamam logon se mujhey ziyada mehbub tha aur uskey baad ye bhi mujhey tamam logon se ziyada mehbub hai.'' aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein bhi isi tarah hai, aur iskey aakhir mein hai : ''main uskey mutalliq tumhen wasiyat karta hun kyonkey wo tumharey sualeheen mein se hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6151,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke azad karda ghulam Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) ko Quran karim ki us aayat '' unko unke baap-daada  ke naam se bulaao.'' ke nazil honey tak ham Zaid bin Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) keh kar bulaya kartey they. muttafaq aleh. aur Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya (أنت منی) ""tum mjhse ho"" (باب بلوغ الصغیر و حضانتہ) mein zikr ho chuki hai."
6152,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par Arfa ke roz aap ki oontni qaswaa par khitab farmatey huey dekha, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''logo ! maine tum mein aisi chiz chhodi hai jab tak tum usey thaamey rakho gey gumrah nahin hogey , wo Allah ki kitab aur meri ""itrat""yani merey ehle-bait hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6153,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tum mein aisi chiz chhod kar ja raha hun jab tak tum uskey sath tamassuk (mazboot talluq) ikhtiyar rakho gey to merey baad kabhi gumrah nahin hogey , in mein se eik dusri se azeem tar hai, Allah ki kitab jo ke eik aisi rassi hai jo aasman se zamin ki taraf daraz ki gaee hai, aur meri ""itrat"" ehle-bait , ye dono alag nahin hongey yahan tak ke hoz (kausar) par merey paas aaeyngey. dekho ke tum un dono ke barey mein meri kaisi jaa-nasheeni nibhaatey ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6154,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali , Fatima aur Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein farmaya : ''jisney in se ladaai ki main us se ladney wala hun, aur jisney un-se musaalihat (samjhota) ki main us se musaalihat (samjhota) karney wala hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6155,"Hazrat Jume bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main apni phuphi ke sath Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya to maine puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sab se ziyada kis se mohabbat thi ? unhoney farmaya : Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) sey, puchha gaya : mardon mein se? unhoney farmaya : unke shohar (Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) se. rawahu Tirmizi."
6156,"Hazrat Abdul Muttalaib bin Rabeea se riwayat hai ke Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ghussey ki haalat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, main us waqt aap ke paas hi tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aap ko kis ne naraz kiya?'' unhoney farmaya : Allah ke Rasool ! hamara (banu Hashim) aur baqi quraishiyon ka kya maamla hai? jab wo aapas mein miltey hain to badi khanda peshani se miltey hain, aur jab ham se miltey hain to is tarah nahin miltey, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi ghussey mein aagey yahan tak ke aap ka chehra Mubarak surkh ho gaya. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! kisi shakhs ke dil mein eman dakhil nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke wo Allah aur uskey Rasool ki khatir tum se mohabbat karey.'' phir farmaya : ''logo ! jisney merey chacha ko aziyat pahunchaai usney mujhey aziyat pahunchaai , aadmi ka chacha uskey baap ke manind hota hai.'' Tirmizi, aur Masaabeh mein Mttalib se marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6157,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abbas mujh se hain aur main un se hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6158,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''jab peer ka din ho to aap aur aap ki aulad merey paas aana , main tumharey liye dua karunga jiskey zariey Allah tumhen aur tumhari aulad ko faeyda pahunchaega.'' ham unke sath aap ki khidmat mein hazir huye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein apni chadar mein lekar dua farmaee : ''aey Allah ! Abbas aur uski aulad ki tamam zahiri aur batni khtaaen maaf farma, unka koi gunah baqi na chhod, aey Allah ! unka saya unki aulad par qaaim farma.'' aur Rizeen ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''aur unki aulad mein khilaafat baqi rakh.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur rizeen."
6159,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Jibrael ko do martaba dekha hai. isi ke saath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke haq mein do martaba dua farmaee. rawahu Tirmizi.
6160,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do martaba unke haq mein dua farmaee ke Allah mujhey hikmat ata farmaey. rawahu Tirmizi.
6161,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) miskinon se mohabbat kiya kartey they, unke yahan betha kartey they aur wo un se baat cheet kiya kartey they. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki kunniyat ''Abul Masaakeen'' rakhi thi. rawahu Tirmizi."
6162,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine Jaafar ko jannat mein farishton ke sath parwaaz kartey huey dekha hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6163,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hasan aur Husain ehle jannat ke jawaanon ke sardar hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6164,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hasan aur Husain dono duniya mein merey do phool hain.'' Tirmizi . ye hadees fasal awwal mein bhi guzar chuki hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
6165,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik raat kisi zarurat ke tehat main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye to aap kisi chiz ko chupaey huey they, main nahin janta tha ke wo kya chiz thi? jab main apney kaam se farigh hua to maine arz kiya : aapney ye kya chiz chupa rakhi hai? aapney kapda uthaya to aap ke dono koolhon par Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye dono merey bete hain, aur meri beti ke bete hain, aey Allah ! main inhen mehbub rakhta hun, to bhi in se mohabbat farma , aur in se mohabbat rakhney waley se bhi mohabbat farma.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6166,"Hazrat Salma bayan karti hain ke main Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaee to wo ro rahi thin, maine kaha : aap kyon ro rahi hain? unhoney farmaya : maine khuwab mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to aap ke sar Mubarak aur dadhi par mitti thi. maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap ka kya haal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main abhi abhi Husain ki shahadat ke waqiey mein hazir hua tha.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6167,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya, aap ke ehle bait mein se kon sa shakhs aap ko sab se ziyada mehbub hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hasan aur Husain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya kartey they : ''merey beton ko bulaao.'' aap unhen choomtey aur unhen apney galey se lagatey.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6168,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein khitab farma rahey they ke achcha Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) aaye , unhoney surkh qameesein pehan rakhi thin, wo chaltey aur gir padtey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member se utrey, unhen uthaya aur unhen apney samney bithaya , phir farmaya : ''Allah ne sach farmaya : ''tumharey amwaal aur aulad baaise fitna hain.'' maine un do bachchon ko chaltey aur girtey huey dekha to main sabr na kar saka yahan tak ke maine apni baat kaat kar unhen utha liya.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
6169,"Hazrat Yaa'la bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Husain mujh se hain aur main Husain se hun, jo shakhs Husain se mohabbat karta hai to Allah us se mohabbat karey aur Husain meri aulad se hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6170,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) seeney se lekar sar tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mushaabihat rakhtey hain jabkey Husain (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us se nichley hissey se mushaabihat rakhtey hain. rawahu Tirmizi."
6171,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine apni walida se kaha : mujhey chhod den ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aap ke sath namaze-Maghrib ada karun, aur aap se darkhast karun ke aap tumharey liye aur merey liye duaaey maghfirat farmaeyn, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , aap ke sath namaze-Maghrib ada ki, aap (nafl) Namaz padhtey rahey yahan tak ke aapney Namaze Isha ada ki, phir aap wapis ghar janey lagey to main bhi aap ke peechhey-peechhey chal diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne meri aawaz suni to farmaya : ''kon hai? kya Huzefa hai'' maine arz kya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tumhari aur tumhari walida ki maghfirat farmaai , kya kaam hai? (phir farmaya) ye eik farishta hai, jo us raat se pehley kabhi zamin par nahin utra , usney apney rab se ijazat talab ki ke wo mujhey salam karey aur mujhey basharat sunaiye ke Fatima ehle jannat ki khawatin ki sardar hain. aur Hasan aur Husain ehle jannat ke jawaanon ke sardar hain.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6172,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney kandhey par uthaey huey they to kisi aadmi ne kaha : aey ladkey ! kya khub sawari hai jis par to sawar hai ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sawar bhi kya khub hai !'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6173,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye saadhey teen hazar wazeefa (3500) muqarrar kiya, aur (apney bete) Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye teen hazar wazeefa muqarrar farmaya to Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apney walid se arz kiya : aapney Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko mujh par kyon foqiyat di hai? Allah ki qism ! unhoney kisi ma'rikey (jang) mein mujh se sabqat hasil nahin ki. unhoney farmaya : isliye ke Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tumharey walid se ziyada mehbub they, aur Usama (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tum se ziyada mehbub they lihaza maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mehbub ko apney mehbub par tarjeeh di hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6174,"Hazrat Jabla bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey bhai Zaid ko merey sath bhej den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo hazir hai, agar wo tumhare sath jana chahey to main usey mana nahin karunga.'' Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main aap par kisi ko tarjeeh nahin deta. unhoney kaha : maine apney bhai ki raey ko apni raey se afzal paya. rawahu Tirmizi."
6175,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (bimari ki wajeh sey) zaeef ho gaey to maine aur Sahaba kiram ne Madina mein rihaaish ikhtiyar karli, chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to us waqt aap khamosh they aur kisi se koi baat nahin kar rahey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh par apney haath Mubarak rakhtey aur unhen utha letey maine jaan liya ke aap merey liye dua kar rahey hain. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6176,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ki naak saaf karna chahi to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya : mujhey ijazat farmaain mein saaf kar deti hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha is se mohabbat kiya karo kyonkey us se main mohabbat karta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6177,"Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darwaze par) betha hua tha ke Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ijazat talab karney ke liye tashrif laye to unhoney Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hamein ijazat ley den, maine (andar ja kar) arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) andar aaney ki ijazat talab kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke wo kyon aaye hain? maine arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''lekin main janta hun, un dono ko ijazat dey do.'' wo dono andar aaye to arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham aap ki khidmat mein ye daryaft karney ke liye hazir huey hain ke aap ko apney ehle khana mein se kis se ziyada mohabbat hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Fatima binte Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam).'' unhoney arz kiya : ham aap ki khidmat mein aap ke ehle khana ke mutalliq poochhney nahin aaye , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey ehle (yani mardon) mein se wo shakhs mujhey ziyada mehbub hai jis par Allah ne inaam farmaya aur maine inaam kiya, Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu).'' unhoney arz kiya, phir kon? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu).'' Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney apney chacha ko un ke baad rakha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' isliye ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se pehley hijrat ki hai.'' Tirmizi . aur ye baat : ''aadmi ka chacha uskey walid ki manind hota hai.'' kitabuz zakat mein guzar chuki hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6178,"Hazrat Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne namaze-Asr padhi , phir bahar nikley to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unke sath chal rahey they, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko bachchon ke sath khelte hue dekha to unhen apney kandhey par utha liya, aur farmaya : merey walid qurban hon, uski Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mushaabihat hai, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se mushaabihat nahin, (ye baat sun kar) Ali (Raziallahu anhu) muskura diye. Bukhari."
6179,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke sar ko Ubaidullah bin Ziyad ke paas laya gaya to usey eik tasht mein rakh diya gaya, wo (chhadi ke sath) maarney laga aur usney unke Husn ke barey mein kuchh kaha, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! wo sab se ziyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mushabeh they, aur us waqt unke sar Mubarak par wasma laga hua tha. Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai, unhoney kaha : main ibne Ziyad ke paas tha ke Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ka sar laya gaya, to wo aap ki naak par chhadi maarney laga , aur kehney laga : maine aisa Husn nahin dekha, maine kaha : sun ley ! ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sab se ziyada mushaabihat rakhtey they. unhoney farmaya : ye hadees sahih Hasan gharib hai. Bukhari aur Tirmizi."
6180,"Hazrat Umme-Fazal binte Haris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine raat eik ajeeb sa khuwab dekha hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo kya hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : wo bahut shadeed hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo kya hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : maine dekha ke goya gosht ka eik tukda hai jo aap ke jisme-paak se kaat kar meri god mein rakh diya gaya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne khair dekhi hai, Insha-Allah Fatima bachchey ko janm dengi aur wo tumhari god mein hoga.'' Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko janm diya aur wo meri god mein tha jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha. eik roz main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to maine Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko aap ki god mein rakh diya. phir main kisi aur taraf mutawajjeh ho gaee , achcha dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aakhon se aansu rawan they, wo bayan karti hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi ! merey waliden aap par qurban hon ! aap ko kya hua? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) merey paas tashrif laye aur unhoney mujhey bataya ke meri ummat an-qareeb merey is bete ko Shahid kar degi. maine kaha : is (bachchey) ko? unhoney kaha : haan ! aur unhoney mujhey us (jagah) ki surkh mitti la kar di.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nabuwa)."
6181,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : maine eik roz nisfun nahar (din ka beech) ke waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khuwab mein dekha ke aap ke baal paraa ganda (bikhre hue) hain aur jisme paak ghubar aalud hai, aap ke haath mein khoon ki botal hai, maine arz kiya, merey waliden aap par qurban hon, ye kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Husain aur unke sathiyon ka khoon hai, main aaj subah se isey ikhatta kar raha hun.'' maine us waqt ko yad rakha aur baad mein mujhey malum hua ke usi waqt unhen Shahid kiya gaya tha. dono hadison ko Behaqi ne dalaeelun nabuwa mein riwayat kiya hai aur aakhiri hadees ko Imam Ahmed ne bhi riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nabuwa aur Ahmed)."
6182,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah se mohabbat karo ke usney tumhen nematon se nawaza hai, aur Allah ki mohabbat ki khatir mujh se mohabbat karo aur meri mohabbat ki khatir merey ehle bait se mohabbat karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6183,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : is haal mein ke wo Kaba ke darwazey ko pakdey huey they, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''sun lo ! tummein merey ehle bait ki misal kashtiye Nuh ki tarah hai, jo is mein Sawar ho gaya wo najat pa gaya aur jo us se reh gaya wo halak ho gaya.'' (rawahu Ahmed)."
6184,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''(apney zamaney mein) Maryam binte Imran sab se behtar khatoon thin, aur (us zamaney mein) Khadija binte Khuwelid sab se behtar khatoon hain.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : Abu-Kuraib bayan kartey hain, Wakee (Raziallahu anhu) ne aasman aur zamin ki taraf ishara farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
6185,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney arz kiya : ''Allah ke Rasool ! Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) aa rahi hain, unke paas eik bartan hai jis mein salan hai aur khana hai, jab wo aap ke paas ayen to unke rab ki taraf se aur meri taraf se unhen salam kehna, aur unhen jannat mein khaul daar moti ke ghar ki basharat dena jis mein koi shor aur shaghab hoga na koi thakan hogi.'' muttafaq aleh."
6186,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi zauja mohtarma ke barey mein itna rashk nahin kiya jitna Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ke mamley mein kiya, halanke maine unhen dekha nahin, lekin aap aksar unka zikr kiya kartey they, kabhi-kabhi aap bakri zibeh kartey phir uskey tukdey kartey phir unhen Khadija ki saheliyon ke yahan bhejtey they, kabhi kabhar main aap se yun arz karti : goya duniya mein Khadija ke siwa koi aurat hi nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''wo aisi thin, wo aisi thin aur un se meri aulad hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6187,"Hazrat Abu-Salma se riwayat hai ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aaisha ! Jibrael (Alaihissalam) tumhen salam kehtey hain.'' unhoney farmaya : w Alehissalam wa Rehmatullah ! aur unhoney farmaya : jo chizen aap dekhtey they wo mujhey nazar nahin aati thin. muttafaq aleh."
6188,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''tum mujhey khuwab mein teen raaten dikhai gaeen. farishta resham ke tukdey main tumhen uthaey huey hai aur usney mujhey kaha : ye aap ki ehliya (biwi) hai, maine tumharey chehrey se kapda uthaya to wo aap thin.'' maine kaha : agar ye (khuwab) Allah ki taraf se hai to wo usey pura farma dega.'' muttafaq aleh."
6189,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Sahaba kiram apney tohfe pesh karney ke liye Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ka din talash kiya kartey they aur wo uskey zariey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khushi hasil karna chahtey they. aur unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyon ke do giroh they, eik giroh mein Aaisha , Hafsa , Safiya aur Sauda (Raziallahu anha) thin jabkey doosrey giroh mein Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baqi paak biviyan thin, Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke giroh ne mashwara kiya aur unhoney Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat karen ke aap logon se farma den ke jo shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hadiya bhejna chahey to wo aap ki khidmat mein wahin hadiya bhejey jahan aap tashrif farma hon. unhon (Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha)) ne aap se baat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''mujhey Aaisha ke barey mein takleef na pahunchaaw, kyonkey Aaisha ke ilawa kisi zauja mohtarma ke kapdey mein mujh par ""wahi"" nahin aati.'' unhon (Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap ko takleef pahunchaney ki wajeh se main Allah ke huzur tauba karti hun. phir unhoney Fatima ko bulaya aur unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf bheja unhoney aap se baat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beti ! kya tum wo chiz pasand nahin karti ho jo main pasand karta hun?'' unhoney arz kiya, kyon nahin, zarur (pasand karti hun) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) se mohabbat karo.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : (Fazal Aaisha Alan Nisa baab badulkhalk) mein Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se zikr ki gaee hai."
6190,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahan ki khawatin mein se (kamaal ke aetbar sey) Maryam binte Imran, Khadija binte Khuwelid, Fatima binte Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Firon ki biwi Aasiya (Raziallahu anhu) tumharey liye kafi hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6191,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Jibrael (Alaihissalam) sabz (hare) reshmi kapdey mein meri tasweer lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kiya : ''ye duniya aur aakhirat mein aap ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
6192,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko pata chala ke Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne (unhen) kaha hai : Yahudi ki beti , wo roney lagin, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas aaye to wo ro rahi thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum kyon ro rahi ho?'' unhoney arz kiya, Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey kaha hai ke main Yahudi ki beti hun, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum eik Nabi ki beti ho, tumhara chacha bhi Nabi aur tum Nabi ki ehliya bhi ho. wo kis barey main tum se fakhr karti hain?'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hafsa ! Allah se darti raho.'' (rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai fil-Kubra)."
6193,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur un se sargoshi farmaee to wo ro padin , phir un se koi baat ki to wo hans padi , jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to maine unke roney aur unki hansi ke mutalliq un se puchha to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bataya tha ke main faut ho jaaunga to main ro padi , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bataya ke Maryam binte Imran ke ilawa ehle jannat ki khawatin ki main sardar hun.'' is par main hans di. rawahu Tirmizi."
6194,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ham par yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba par jab bhi koi hadees shubah mein pad jati to ham Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft kartey to ham uskey mutalliq unke yahan ilm paatey they. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6195,Hazrat Musa bin Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne fasaahat aur balaaghat mein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se badh kar kisi ko nahin dekha. isey Imam Tirmizi ne riwayat kiya hai aur isey Hasan sahih gharib kaha hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
6196,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine khuwab mein dekha ke goya merey haath mein resham ka eik tukda hai, main jannat mein jis jagah janey ka qasd (irada) (irada) karta hun to wo mujhey uda kar wahan ley jata hai, maine Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se uska zikr kiya to Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara bhai nek aadmi hai.'' ya farmaya : ''Abdullah nek aadmi hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6197,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, chaal dhaal aur seerat aur hidayaat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sab se ziyada mushabeh ibne Umme-Abd (Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) hain, aur unke ghar se nikalney se lekar wapis ghar janey tak yehi surat rehti hai, jab wo apney ehle khana ke sath khilwat mein hotey hain to malum nahin wo kya kartey hain? Bukhari."
6198,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur mera bhai Yamen se wapis aaye to kuchh muddat tak ham yehi samajhtey rahey ke Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehle bait ke eik fard hain. wo isliye ke unka aur unki walida ka ba-kasrat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aana jana ham dekha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
6199,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaar hazraat , Abdullah bin Masood , Abu-Huzaifa ke azad karda ghulam Saalim, Ubai bin Kab aur Muaz bin Jabal se Quran ki taalim hasil karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
6200,"Hazrat Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Sham pahuncha to maine do rakaat Namaz padh kar dua ki : aey Allah ! mujhey kisi Saleh sathi ka saath nasib farma, main logon ke paas aaya aur unke paas beth gaya, chunanche eik buzurg aaye aur wo merey pehlu mein beth gaey, maine kaha : ye kon sahab hain? unhoney bataya : Abu-Darda hain, maine kaha : maine Allah se dua ki thi ke wo mujhey kisi Saleh shakhs ka saath nasib farmaai to usney mujhey aap ki ham-nasheenin ata farmaey. unhoney mujh se puchha : aap kon hain? maine kaha : koofi hun, unhoney kaha : kya tumharey yahan ibn Umme- Abd (Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) jutiyon wale sahib, saada aur paak (nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jutiyan uthaney waley, aap ka bistar durust karney waley aur aap ke wuzu ke liye pani ka ehtimam karney waley) nahin hain? aur tum mein wo bhi hain jinhen Allah ne apney Nabi ki dua ke zariey shetan se panah de-di hai yani Ammar bin Yasir, kya tum mein Raz-daan nahin hain? un raazon ko unke siwa koi nahin janta yani Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu). Bukhari."
6201,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey jannat dikhai gaee, maine Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya dekhin , aur apney aagey Bilal ke jooton ki aawaz suni.'' rawahu Muslim."
6202,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham chhe afrad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, mushrekin ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha ke un logon ko yahan se door kar do aur ye hamari mojudgi mein aaney ki jurrat na karen, raawi bayan kartey hain (un mein) main, ibne-Masood, Huzail qabiley ka eik aadmi, Bilal aur do aadmi aur they jin ka main naam nahin leta, Allah ne jo chaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke dil mein khayal aaya aur aapney apney dil mein koi baat sochi to Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''aap un logon ko door na karen jo subah aur Sham apney rab ko, uski razamandi ko hasil karne ke liye pukartey rehtey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
6203,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''Abu-Musa ! aap ko aale Dawud ki si behatareen awaaz ata ki gaee hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
6204,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein chaar afrad ne Quran ko jama kar liya tha : Ubai bin Kab , Muaz bin Jabal , Zaid bin Sabit aur Abu-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) , Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya : Abu-Zaid kon hain? unhoney farmaya : merey eik chacha hain. muttafaq aleh."
6205,"Hazrat Khabbab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath hijrat ki, ham Allah ki razamandi chahtey they, chunanche hamara ajr Allah ke yahan Sabit ho gaya, ham mein se kuchh (jald) wafat pa gaey aur unhoney apney (dunyawi) ajr (maale-ghanimat waghera) se kuchh na paya, Musab bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhi mein se hain, wo ghazwae uhad mein Shahid ho gaey they, unhen kafan deney ke liye sirf eik dhaari daar chadar muyassar aai , jab ham unka sar dhaanptey to unke dono paaon nangey ho jatey aur jab ham unke dono paaon dhaanptey to unka sar nanga ho jata, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us se unka sar dhanp do aur unke paaon par ghaas dal do.'' aur ham mein se wo bhi hain ke unke liye phal pak chukey hain aur wo unhen chun rahey hain. (futoohaat (jeet) ke baad dunyawi fawaaid bhi hasil kar rahey hain) muttafaq aleh."
6206,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat par arsh hal gaya tha.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut par Rehman ka arsh hil gaya tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
6207,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein reshmi joda bator hadiya pesh kya gaya to Sahaba usey chhooney lagey aur uski mulaimiyat par tajjub karney lagey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum uski mulaimiyat par tajjub kartey ho. Saad bin Muaz ke jannat mein rumaal is se ziyada behtar hain aur ziyada mulayem hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
6208,"Hazrat umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! Anas (Raziallahu anhu) aap ka khaadim hai, uskey liye Allah se dua farmaain : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! uskey maal w aulad mein izafa farma , aur tu ney jo usey ata farmaya hai is mein barkat farma .'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mera maal bahut ziyada hai, aur aaj merey bete aur merey potey so se ziyada hain. muttafaq aleh."
6209,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ke ilawa roey zamin par chalney waley kisi aur shakhs ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey nahin suna ke '' wo ehle jannat mein se hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6210,"Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Madina ki masjid mein betha hua tha ke eik aadmi aaya uskey chehrey par khushu ke aasaar they. haazirin ne kaha : ye aadmi ehle jannat mein se hai, chunanche usney ikhtisaar ke sath do rakatein padhin, phir wo chala gaya. main uskey peechey peechey gaya, to maine kaha : jis waqt aap masjid mein tashrif laye they to logon ne kaha tha ke ye aadmi ehle jannat mein se hai. us aadmi ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! kisi shakhs ke liye munasib nahin ke wo aisi baat kahey jisey wo janta nahin, main tumhen batata hun ke aisey kyon hai maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein khuwab dekha to maine usey aap se bayan kya : maine dekha ke goya main eik baagh mein hun, unhoney uski wusat aur uski shadabi ka zikr kya, uskey wast mein lohey ka sutoon hai, uska nichlaa hissey zamin mein hai aur uska ooper wala hissey aasman mein hai, uski choti par eik halqa ( kada ( hai, mujhey kaha gaya is par chadho , maine kaha : main istataat nahin rakhta , merey paas eik khaadim aaya usney peechey se merey kapdey uthaey to main ooper chadh gaya, yahan tak ke maine uski choti par pahunch kar halqey ( kadey ( ko pakad liya , mujhey kaha gaya : mazbuti ke sath pakad lo, mein usey pakdey huey tha ke main bedaar ho gaya, maine usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo baagh Islam hai, aur wo sutoon Islam ka sutoon hai aur wo halqa mazbut halqa hai tum martey dam tak Islam par rahogey.'' aur wo aadmi Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) they. muttafaq aleh."
6211,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sabit bin Qais bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) ansaar ke khateeb they, chunanche jab ye aayat : ''aey eman walo! apni aawaazon ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aawaz se buland na karo.'' nazil hui to Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) apney ghar mein beth gaey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aana band kar diya. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ka kya maamla hai kya wo bimar hai?'' Saad (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo kaha tha uskey mutalliq unhen bataya to Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye aayat nazil hui aur tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney meri aawaz tum sab se ziyada buland hoti hai, lihaza main (is aayat ke mutabiq) jahannamiyon mein se hon, Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin ( aisey nahin) balke wo to ehle jannat mein se hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
6212,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Sura Juma nazil hui to ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bethey huey they, jab ye aayat ( وَاخَرِیْنَ مِنْھُمْ لَمَّا یَلْحَقُوْا بِھِمْ ( nazil hui to ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! un se kon log murad hain? raawi bayan kartey hain, Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey darmiyan mojud they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Salman (Raziallahu anhu) par apna daste-mubarak rakh kar farmaya : ''agar eman surayya par bhi hoga to tab bhi un logon mein se kuch hazraat us tak pahunch jaeyngey.'' muttafaq aleh."
6213,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah! apney us bandey yani Abu-Hurera aur unki walida ko apney momin bandon ka mehbub bana dey aur mominon ko unka mehbub bana dey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
6214,"Hazrat aaid bin Amr se riwayat hai ke abu-Sufiyaan Salman, Suheb aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey us waqt aur Sahaba kiram bhi mojud they, unhoney kaha : Allah ki talwaaron ne Allah ke dushman ki gardan se apna haq wasul nahin kya. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya tum aisi baat Quraish ke moatabar aur sardar shakhs ke barey mein kehtey ho? abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur unhen bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu-Bakar! shayad ke tum ne unhen naraz kar diya hai, agar tum ne unhen naraz kya to tum ne apney rab ko naraz kar diya.'' wo unke paas aaye aur kaha : bhaaiyo ! kya maine tumhen naraz kar diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin, bhai ! Allah aap ki maghfirat farmaey. rawahu Muslim."
6215,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ansaar se mohabbat alamat eman hai, aur adawat ansaar alamate-nifaq hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6216,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' ansaar se sirf momin shakhs hi mohabbat karta hai jabkey ansaar se sirf munafiq shakhs hi adawat rakhta hai, chunanche jisney un se mohabbat ki to Allah us se mohabbat kerega aur jisney un se adawat ki to Allah us se adawat kerega .'' muttafaq aleh."
6217,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Allah ne apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hawazin qabiley ke amwaal mein se ghanimat ata farmaai aur aap Quraish ke (new Muslim) afrad ko so oont deney lagey to ansaar ke kuch logon ne kaha : Allah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki maghfirat farmaai , aap qureshiyon ko to ata farma rahey hain jabkey hamen chhod rahey hain, aur soorate-haal ye hai ke hamari talwaaron se unka khoon abhi tak tapak raha hai, unki ye guftgu Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko batai gaee to aapney ansaar ko bula bheja aur unhen chamdey ke eik khemey mein jama kya aur aapney unke ilawa kisi aur ko wahan na bulaya, jab wo ikhattey ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : '' tumharey mutalliq mujhey kya khabar pahunchi hai? '' un ( ansaar (ke samajhdaar logon ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey sanjeeda logon ne to koi baat nahin ki, albatta hamarey chand no umr ladkon ne kaha hai : Allah , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko maaf farmaai ke wo Qureshiyon ko dey rahey hain aur ansaar ko chhod rahey hain, jabkey hamari talwaaron se un (Qureshiyon) ka khoon tapak raha hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine naey muslimon ko unki taaleef-qalbi ke liye diya hai, kya tum pasand nahin kartey ke log to maal w dolat lekar wapis jaeyn aur tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sath lekar apney gharon ko wapis jaao.'' unhoney arz kya, kyon nahin, Allah ke Rasool! ham is par razi hain. muttafaq aleh."
6218,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar hijrat na hoti to main bhi ansaar mein se eik aadmi hota, agar sarey log eik wadi mein chalen aur ansaar eik wadi ya ghaati mein chalen to main bhi ansaar ki wadi aur ghaati mein chalunga, ansaar astar hain jabkey baqi log ooper ka kapda hain, be-shak tum log merey baad tarjeeh dekhogey (ke tum par dusron ko tarjeeh di jaeygi ( tum sabr karna yahan tak ke tum hoz kausar par mujh se mulaqat karo.'' Bukhari ."
6219,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Fateh Makka ke roz ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs abu-Sufiyaan ke ghar dakhil ho jaey to wo aman mein hai, jo hathiyar dal dey wo aman mein hai.'' ansaar ne kaha is aadmi ko apney rishtedaron se rehmat aur apney shehar ki mohabbat ne pakad liya , ( unki is baat ke mutalliq ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par wahi nazil hui to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kaha hai ke us aadmi ko apney kunbey se shafqat aur apney shehar se mohabbat ne pakad liya hai, sun lo , aisey nahin, mein Allah ka banda aur uska Rasool hun, maine Allah aur tumhari taraf hijrat ki, mera jeena marna tumharey sath hai.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ki qism ! ham ne to mehaz Allah aur uskey Rasool ki rafaqat ke husool ke liye aisey kaha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah aur uska Rasool tumhari tasdeeq kartey hain aur tumhara uzr qubul kartey rahen.'' rawahu Muslim ."
6220,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( ansaar ke) kuch bachon aur khawatin ko kisi shaadi ki taqreeb se wapis aatey huey dekha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khadey ho kar farmaya : ''aey Allah ! ( to janta hai) tum tamam logon se ziyada mujhey mehbub ho, aey Allah ! (to janta hai) tum yani ansaar tamam logon se ziyada mujhey mehbub ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
6221,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Bakar aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ansaar ki eik majlis ke paas se guzrey to wo us waqt ro rahey they. unhoney puchha : tum kyon ro rahey ho? unhoney kaha : ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis ko yad kya jis mein ham ( betha kartey ( they, un dono mein se eik Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney uskey mutalliq aap ko bataya , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sar Mubarak par kapdey ki patti baandhey huey bahar tashrif laye aur member par jalwa afroz huye, aur us roz ke baad aap member par tashrif na la sakey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah Taala ki hamd w sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''main ansaar ke barey main tumhen wasiyat karta hun, wo merey jism w jaan ( dast w bazu ( hain, wo apni zimme-daariyan nibha chukey, ab unke huquq baqi hain, tum unke nek logon ki taraf se (uzr) qubul karna aur unke Khatakaron se darguzar karna.'' Bukhari ."
6222,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney marze-wafat mein bahar tashrif laye aur member par jalwa afroz huye, aapney Allah ki hamd w sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''baqi log to bahut ziyada ho jaeyngey jabkey ansaar kam ho jaeyngey yahan tak ke wo logon mein namak ke tanaasub se ho jaeyngey, tum mein se jo shakhs kisi aisi chiz ka zimmedar w sarparast ho jis mein wo kisi nuqsan aur kisi ko faeyda pahuncha sakta ho to wo un ( ansaar (ke nekon ke nek kamon ko qubul karey aur unke Khatakaron se darguzar karey.'' Bukhari ."
6223,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! ansaar, ansaar ki aulad aur ansaar ki aulad ki aulad ki maghfirat farma.'' rawahu Muslim ."
6224,"Hazrat abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ansaar ka sab se behtareen qabila bano najaar ka qabila hai, phir bano Abdul-Ash'hal, bano Haris bin khazraj, phir bano saaida aur ansaar ke her qabiley mein khair hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6225,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh ko , Zuber aur Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) ko , eik dusri riwayat mein Miqdad ke bajaey Abu-Marsad (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam hai, kisi kaam par rawana farmaya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum chaltey jana yahan tak ke tum rauza khaakh par pahunch jaao , wahan eik aurat hogi uskey paas eik khat hoga tum wo us se ley lena .'' ham rawana huye, ham apney ghodey daudaatey rahey yahan tak ke ham rauza khaakh par pahunch gaey, aur wahan hamen wo aurat mil gaee . ham ne kaha : khat nikalo , usney kaha : merey paas koi khat nahin, ham ne kaha : khat nikal do warna ham terey kapdey utaar dengey, chunanche usney wo khat apni choti se nikal diya, ham wo khat lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to is mein likha hua tha, Haatib bin abi Baltaa ki taraf se ehle-Makka ke chand mushrekin ke naam, unhoney is mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baaz baton ke mutalliq unhen khabar di thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Haatib ye kya (maajra) hai? '' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! merey mutalliq jaldi na farmana , main eik aisa shakhs hun ke main Quraish ka haleef hun, main unke khandan mein se nahin hun, aur aap ke sath jo muhajrin hain, unki to ( un sey) qurbat hai jiski wajeh se wo Makka mein unke amwaal aur ehle w ayaal ki hifazat kar rahey hain, maine un se nasbi rishta na honey ki wajeh se ye pasand kya ke main un se koi ehsan karun, jiski wajeh se wo merey qurbat daaron ki hifazat karengey . maine ye kufr ki wajeh se kya hai na apney Deen se irtidad ki wajeh se kya hai aur na hi Islam ke baad kufr ko pasand karkey kya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usney tum se sachi baat ki hai.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey ijazat farmaain mein us munafiq ki gardan uda dun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us shakhs ne ghazwae-Badr mein shirkat ki hai, aur tum nahin jantey ke Allah ne ehle Badr ke ahwaal pehley se jaan liye they, isliye usney farmaya : ''jo chaho so karo, tumharey liye jannat wajib ho chuki hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''main tumhen maaf kar chuka .'' tab Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmaai: ''emaan walo ! merey aur apney dushmanon ko dost na banaao.'' muttafaq aleh."
6226,"Hazrat Rifa bin Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney farmaya : ''tum ehle Badr ko apney yahan kis darjey mein shumar kartey ho ?'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalmanon mein se sab se afzal .'' ya aapney isi tarah ki baat farmaai .'' unhon ( Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ( ne farmaya : '' isi tarah jo farishtey Badr mein shareek huey unka bhi buland darja hai.'' Bukhari ."
6227,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ummid karta hun ke inshaAllah ghazwa Badr aur suleh-Hudebiya mein shirkat karney wala koi shakhs jahannam mein dakhil nahin hoga.'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah Taala ne to farmaya hai : ''tum mein se her shakhs ne is par waarid hona hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne suna nahin, wo farmata hai : phir wo taqwa ikhtiyar karney walon ko bacha lega .'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''insha Allah as-haab shajra jinhon ne us (darkht) ke nichey baiat ki thi jahannam mein dakhil nahin hongey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
6228,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : suleh Hudebiya ke moqe par ham chaudah so afrad they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen farmaya : '' aaj zamin walon mein se tum sab se behtar ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
6229,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs saniyatul-Marar ki choti par chadhega to uskey gunah is tarah khatam kar diye jaeyngey jis tarah bani-Israel ke gunah khatam kar diye gaey they.'' bano khazraj ka dasta sab se pehley is par chadha, phir baqi log mutawatir pahunchtey rahey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us surkh oont waley ke siwa tum sab ki maghfirat ho gaee.'' ham us shakhs ke paas aaye to ham ne kaha : aao Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumharey liye maghfirat talab karen, usney kaha : agar main apna gum shuda oont pa lun to ye mujhey us se ziyada pasand hai ke tumhara sathi merey liye maghfirat talab karey. rawahu Muslim . aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke ''Allah ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen Quran sunaaun.'' (baab fazaailul-Quran) ke baad zikr ki gaee hai."
6230,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey baad merey do Sahaba abu-Bakar w umr ki iqtida (pairvi) karna , Ammar ki raah par chalna , Umme- abd ( Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ki wasiyat ko lazim pakadna.'' Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : '' ibne-Masood jo baat tum se kahin uski tasdeeq karna.'' is mein ibn Umme-abd ( Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ki wasiyat ko lazim pakadna.'' ke alfaz ke bajaey mazkura baala alfaz hain. rawahu Tirmizi ."
6231,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main kisi mashware ke baghair kisi shakhs ko ameer muqarrar karta to main ibn Umme- abd ( Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ko unka ameer muqarrar karta .'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
6232,"Hazrat khaisma bin abi sabra bayan kartey hain, main Madina aaya to maine Allah se darkhast ki wo kisi Saleh shakhs ki ham nasheenon ikhtiyar karney ki tofiq bakhshey , chunanche usney merey liye Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki ham nasheenon muyassar farma di, main unke paas beth gaya, maine kaha : maine Allah se dua ki thi ke wo mujhey kisi Saleh shakhs ki ham nasheenon muyassar farmaai , mujhey tumhari ham nasheenon nasib hui hai. unhoney farmaya : tum kahan se ( aaye ( ho? maine kaha koofa se aur main khair ki talab w talash mein aaya hun. unhoney farmaya : kya tum mein mustajaabuddawaat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) nahin hain? aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tahaarat ke liye wuzu ka intizam karney waley aur aap ke jootey uthaney waley ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) nahin hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke razdaan Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) jinhen Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban par shetan se panah di hai, aur sahab kitaabain yani Injeel w Quran par eman rakhney waley Salman nahin hain? rawahu Tirmizi."
6233,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achcha shakhs hai abu-Bakar, achcha shakhs hai umr, achcha shakhs hai abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah, achcha shakhs hai Usaid bin Huzair, behtareen aadmi hai Sabit bin Qais bin shamaas, behtareen aadmi hai Muaz bin Jabal aur achcha shakhs hai Muaz bin Amr bin jamooh (Raziallahu anhu).'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6234,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat teen ashkhaas, Ali, Ammar aur Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ki mushtaaq hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
6235,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen ijazat dey do. bahut hi achey shakhs ke liye khush aamadeed.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
6236,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ammar ko jab bhi do umur (baton) mein se kisi eik ko pasand karney ka ikhtiyar diya gaya to unhoney un mein se mushkil kaam ko pasand kya. '' rawahu Tirmizi ."
6237,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza uthaya gaya to munafiqon ne kaha : uska janaza kis qadr halka hai, aur ye banu-Qureza ke mutalliq uskey faisley ki wajeh se hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak baat pahunchi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' halka isliye hai ke farishtey usey uthaey huey they.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
6238,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' aasman roey zamin par Abu-Zar se ziyada sacha aadmi koi nahin.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
6239,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aasman tuley roey zamin par Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se ziyada raast bhale hi aur ehade-wafaa karney wala aur zuhud mein Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) se ziyada mushabeh koi nahin.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
6240,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, jab unki maut ka waqt qarib aaya to unhoney kaha : chaar ashkhaas se ilm hasil karo, Uwemir abu-Darda Salman , ibne-Masood aur Abdullah bin Salam se aur Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) Yahudi they, phir Islam qubul kya, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' aap das jannatiyon mein se daswein hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
6241,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! agar aap khalifa muqarrar farma den? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar maine tum par khalifa muqarrar kar diya aur tum ne uski nafarmani ki to tum azab mein mubtala ho jaaogey, lekin Huzefa jo tumhen bataeyn uski tasdeeq karo aur Abdullah jo tumhen padhaein usey padho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6242,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ke ilawa her shakhs ke mutalliq andesha hai ke usey fitna nuqsan pahunchaega, lekin unke mutalliq koi andesha nahin kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''fitna tumhen nuqsan nahin pahunchaega.'' sanad zaeef rawahu Abu-Dawood."
6243,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein chiragh jalta hua dekha to farmaya : ''Aaisha ! mera khayal hai ke Asma ke yahan wiladat hui hai, tum us bachchey ka naam na rakhna , uska naam mein khud rakhunga.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us (bachchey) ka naam Abdullah rakha aur apney haath se khajoor ke sath usey ghatii di. rawahu Tirmizi."
6244,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq farmaya : ''aey Allah ! isey haadi aur hidayat yafta bana aur iskey zariey hidayat nasib farma.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
6245,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ne Islam qubul kiya aur Amr bin Aas eman laye.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. iski sanad qawi nahin. rawahu Tirmizi."
6246,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se mulaqat ki to farmaya : ''Jabir ! kya baat hai ke main tumhen gham mein dekh raha hun?'' maine arz kiya : merey walid Shahid ho gaey hain aur unhoney bachchey aur qarz chhoda hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen us chiz ke mutalliq khushkhabri na sunaaun jiskey sath Allah ne terey walid se mulaqat farmaee?'' maine arz kiya, zarur Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne jis se bhi kalam farmaya , isliye pardae se kalam farmaya, aur terey walid ko zinda kiya to us se hijaab ke baghair kalam farmaya, farmaya : merey bandey ! tamanna kar , main tujhey ata karunga. unhoney arz kiya : rab ji ! to mujhey zinda farma ta ke main teri khaatir dobara Shahid kar diya jaaun , Rab Tabarak w taala ne farmaya : meri taraf se faisla ho chuka hai ke wo wapis nahin jaeyngey.'' tab ye aayat nazil hui : ''Allah ki raah mein Shahid ho janey walon ko murda mat kaho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6247,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey liye pachchis martaba maghfirat talab ki. rawahu Tirmizi."
6248,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kitney hi log hain jo paraa ganda (bikhre) baal hain, ghubar aalud hain un par do boseedah kapdey hain, unki koi waqat (izzat) nahin hoti lekin agar wo Allah par qism utha lein to wo usey puri farma deta hai, Bara bin Maalik bhi unhi mein se hain.'' (rawahu Tirmizi aur al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
6249,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! merey ehle-bait merey khas hain jahan main panah leta hun, aur merey raz-daan ansaar hain, unke Khataakaaron se darguzar karo aur unke nekukaron se (uzr) qubul karo.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6250,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah aur roze-aakhirat par eman rakhney wala koi shakhs ansaar se dushmani nahin rakhega.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6251,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu), Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''apni qom ko salam kaho , kyonkey wo sawal karney se parhez kartey hain aur ladaai ke waqt sabr kartey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6252,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) ka ghulam Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney aap se Haatib ki shikayat kartey huey kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! Haatib jahannam mein jaeyga . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu jhoot kehta hai, wo is mein dakhil nahin hoga. kyonkey wo Badr aur Hudebiya mein shirkat kar chuka hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
6253,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''agar tum phir gaey to Allah tumhari jagah dusri qom ley aaeyga , phir wo tumhari manind nahin hongey.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye kon log hain jinka Allah ne zikr farmaya hai ke agar ham phir gaey to wo hamari jagah aa jaeyngey aur wo hamari tarah nahin hongey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) ki raan par haath maar kar farmaya : ''ye aur inki qom , agar Deen surayyaa par bhi hua to Farsi log usey hasil kar lengey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6254,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ajmiyon ka zikr kiya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main un par ya unke baaz logon par tum se ya tumharey baaz logon se ziyada aitimad karta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6255,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ke saat (7) barguzeeda (paakiza) nigehban hotey hain, jabkey mujhey chaudah ata kiye gaey hain, ham ne arz kiya, wo kon hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aur merey do bete (Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu)), Jaafar, Hamza, Abu-Bakar, Umar, Musab bin Umair, Bilal, Salman, Ammar, Abdullah bin Masood, Abu-Zar aur Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu).'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6256,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, merey aur Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmiyan kisi maamle mein mukaalma (baatcheet) ho gaya to maine un se sakht lehje mein baat ki to Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se meri shikayat laganey chaley gaey, Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ki shikayat kar rahey they, raawi bayan kartey hain, Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) un se sakht lehje mein baat karney lagey aur us sakhti mein izafa hota chala gaya jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh hain koi baat nahin kar rahey, (us par) Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ro padey aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap inhen dekh nahin rahey? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna sar Mubarak utha kar farmaya : ''jisney Ammar se adawat rakhi Allah us se adawat rakhega aur jo shakhs Ammar se bughz rakhega to Allah us se bughz rakhega.'' Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain main wahan se nikla to Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki razamandi ke siwa mujhey koi chiz ziyada mehbub nahin thi. maine unhen razi karney ki koshish ki yahan tak ke wo razi ho gaey. rawahu Ahmed."
6257,"Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Khalid Shan Wale Allah ki talwaaron mein se eik talwaar hain, aur apney qabiley ke achchhey nojawan hain.'' dono hadiso ko Imam Ahmed ne riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed."
6258,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tabarak w taala ne chaar shkhason se mohabbat karney ka mujhey hukm farmaya hai, aur usney mujhey bataya ke wo bhi un se mohabbat karta hai.'' arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! hamein unke naam bata den , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ali un mein se hain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen baar unka naam liya.''  (baqi) Abu-Zar, Miqdad aur Salman hain, usney mujhey un se mohabbat karney ka hukm farmaya hai aur usney mujhey khabar di hai ke wo un se mohabbat karta hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6259,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : hamarey sardar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamarey Sardar yani Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko azad kiya. Bukhari."
6260,"Hazrat Qais bin Abi Hazim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : agar to aapney mujhey apni zaat ke liye kharid hai to phir aap mujhey rok rakhen , aur agar aapney mujhey Allah ki khatir kharid hai to phir mujhey chhod den aur Allah ke raastey mein amal karney den. Bukhari."
6261,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya, mujhey shadeed bhook lagi hui hai, chunanche aapney apni kisi zauja mohtarma ke paas pegham bheja to unhoney arz kiya is zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai ! merey paas to sirf pani hai phir aapney dusri mohtarma ke paas pegham bheja to usney bhi isi tarah kaha, aur tamam paak biviyon ne yehi jawab diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo iski mehman nawaazi karega Allah is par rehem farmaeyga.'' ansaar mein se Abu-Talha naami eik aadmi khada hua aur usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool main, wo usey apney ghar ley gaey aur apni ehliya (biwi) se farmaya : kya tumharey paas (khaney ke liye) koi chiz hai? usney kaha : sirf merey bachchon ke liye khana hai, unhoney farmaya : kisi chiz ke zariey unhen dilaasaa de-kar sulaa do. jab hamara mehman dakhil ho to usey zahir karna ke ham kha rahey hain, jab wo khaney ke liye apna haath badhaey to chiragh durust karney ke bahaney usey bujha dena, chunanche unhoney aisey hi kiya, wo beth gaey, mehman ne khana kha liya aur un dono (miyan biwi) ne bhookey reh kar raat basar ki, jab subah ke waqt wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne falan mard aur falan aurat (ki qurbaani) par tajjub farmaya , ya Allah un dono par hans pada.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aapney Abu-Talha ka naam nahin liya , aur us riwayat ke aakhir mein hai : Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''wo apni jaanon par doosrey ko tarjeeh detey hain agar-che unhen khud bhi zarurat hoti hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6262,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik jagah padaaw dala to log idhar-udhar phirney lagey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''Abu-Huraira ! ye kon hai? ''main arz karta : falan hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''ye Allah ka banda achchhaa hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) poochhtey : ''ye kon hai?'' main arz karta : falan hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''ye Allah ka banda bura hai.'' yahan tak ke Khalid bin Waleed guzrey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon hai?'' maine arz kiya : Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka banda Khalid bin Waleed achchha hai, wo Allah ki talwaaron mein se eik talwaar hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6263,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ansaar ne arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi ! her Nabi ke perokar hotey hain, ham ne bhi aap ki ittiba ki hai, aap Allah se dua farmaain ke wo hamarey muttabaeen ko ham mein shareek farma dey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski dua farmaee. Bukhari."
6264,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham qabaayele-arab mein se koi aisa qabila nahin jantey jiskey shuhda ki tadaad ansaar se ziyada ho, roze-qiyamat sab se ziyada moazziz qabila ansaar ka qabila hoga. raawi bayan kartey hain, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ghazwae uhad mein unke sattar aadmi Shahid huye, beeri-maoona ke waqiey mein sattar Shahid huye, aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ehad mein yamaama ki ladaai mein sattar Shahid huey. Bukhari."
6265,"Hazrat Qais bin Abi Hazim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae Badr mein shareek honey waley Sahaba kiram ka wazeefa paanch paanch hazar tha, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main unko unke baad walon par fazilat dunga. Bukhari."
6266,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Yamen se Ovais naami shakhs tumharey paas aaeyga , wo Yamen mein sirf apni walida ko chhod aaeyga , usey baras tha, usney Allah se dua ki to usney Dinar ya dirham ke barabar jagah ke ilawa us marz ko khatam kar diya, jo shakhs us se mulaqat karey to wo tumharey liye us se duaaey maghfirat ki darkhast karey.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''taabea'iin mein se sab se behtar shakhs Ovais hai, uski walida hai, usey baras ka marz tha, tum us se darkhast karna ke wo tumharey liye duaaey maghfirat karey.'' rawahu Muslim."
6267,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Yamen waley tumharey paas aaye hain, wo raqiqul qalb (halkey dil wala) aur naram dil hain, eman Yamen walon ka hai aur hikmat bhi Yamen walon ki hai, fakhr aur ghurur oont walon mein hota hai jabkey sakeenat aur waqar bakri walon mein hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6268,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kufr ka sar-chashma mashriq mein hai, fakhr aur ghurur ghodey walon , oont walon aur jaagir-daaron jo oont ke baalon se baney huey khemon mein rehtey hain un mein hota hai, aur sakeenat bakri walon mein hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
6269,"Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us taraf yani mashriq ki taraf se fitney namoodaar hongey, jafaa aur sakht dili, jangal mein rehney waley, khema nasheen Rabeea aur Muzar (qabeelon) se talluq rakhney waley un logon mein hogi jo oonton aur bailon ki dumon ke peechhey chal rahey hongey.'' muttafaq aleh."
6270,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dilon ki sakhti aur jafaa mashriq walon mein hai, aur eman ehle hijaaz mein hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
6271,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! hamarey Sham mein barkat farma , aey Allah ! hamarey Yamen mein barkat farma.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey Najad mein , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! hamarey Sham mein barkat farma , aey Allah ! hamarey Yamen mein barkat farma.'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey Najad mein , mera khayal hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teesri martaba farmaya : '' wahan zalzaley aur fitney hongey aur shetan ka seeng wahin se tulu hoga .'' Bukhari."
6272,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Yamen ki taraf dekha to farmaya : ''aey Allah ! unke dilon ko (hamari taraf) mutawajjeh farma , aur hamarey saa aur hamarey mud mein barkat farma.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6273,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shaam ke liye khushhali hai.'' ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye kis wajeh se hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyonkey Rehman ke farishtey is par apney par phelaey huey hain.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
6274,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hizre-maut ki taraf se ya Hizre-Maut se aag niklegi wo logon ko ikhatta karegi.'' ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap hamein kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Sham ki raah ikhtiyar karna.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6275,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''an-qareeb hijrat ke baad hijrat hogi , behtareen log wo hongey jo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki jagah (Shaam) ki taraf hijrat karengey.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''zameen walon mein se sab se behtar log wo hongey jinkey ziyada tar log Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki hijrat ki jagah (Shaam) ki taraf hijrat karengey , aur zamin par bad-tareen log reh jaeyngey, unki araazi unhen phenk dengi , Allah unhen napasand farmaeyga , aag unhen bandaron aur khinzeeron ke sath ikhatta karegi wo (aag) unke sath raat basar karegi , jab wo raat basar karengey , aur jab wo qailula karengey to wo unke sath qailula karegi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
6276,"Hazrat ibne Hawala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb Amr (maamla) (Amr Islam ya Amr qitaal (jang)) is tarah hoga ke tum lashkaron ka majmua hogey , eik lashkar Sham mein hoga, eik lashkar Yamen mein aur eik lashkar Iraq mein.'' ibne Hawala (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar main ye soorate haal pa lun to aap merey liye kis lashkar ka intikhaab farma den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Sham ke lashkar ko lazim pakadnaa, kyonkey wo Allah ki sarzameen main eik pasandida khitta hai aur wo apney pasandida bandon ko uski taraf layega, haan agar tum wahan na jaao to phir tum Yamen ka rukh karna aur apney hauzon se sairab hona kyonkey Allah ne Sham aur ahle-Sham ki muhafizat ki mujhey zamanat di hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
6277,"Hazrat Shureh bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ahle-Sham ka zikr kiya gaya aur arz kiya gaya, Ameerul-momineen ! un par lanat bhejein , unhoney farmaya : nahin, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''abdaal Sham mein hongey, aur wo chaalis afrad hain jab eik aadmi faut ho jaeyga to Allah uski jagah doosrey aadmi ko ley aaeyga , unki wajeh se barish barasti hai, unke zariey dushmanon se badla liya jata hai aur unki wajeh se Sham se azab door kar diya jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
6278,"Hazrat Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mein se eik aadmi se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sarzameene Sham Fateh hogi , agar tumhen wahan kisi jagah ko pasand karney ka ikhtiyar diya jaey to phir dimashq naami jagah ko pasand karna , kyonkey wo Harab aur qitaal (jang) se musalmanon ki jaey-panah (panah ki jagah) hai aur uska bada shehar hai, wahan eik jagah hai jisey al ghuta kaha jata hai.'' dono hadison ko Imam Ahmed ne riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed ."
6279,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khilaafat Madina mein hai jabkey badshahat Sham mein hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
6280,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine apney sar ke nichey se nooraani sutoon nikalta hua dekha aur wo ooper ko buland hua yahan tak ke wo Sham mein ja thehra.'' dono riwayaat ko Imam Behaqi ne dalaeelun nubuwa mein riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
6281,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jang aur jadl ke din musalmanon ka giroh dimashq naami shehar ki janib alghuta ke maqam par hoga, ye Sham ka sab se behtareen shehar hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
6282,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) bayan kartey hain, ajmi badshah zahir hoga to wo dimashq ke ilawa tamam shehron par ghalib aa jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
6283,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhara zamana pichchhli ummaton ke muqabley mein aisa hai jaisey namaze-Asr se ghurub aaftaab tak ka waqt hai, aur tumhari misaal aur yahood aur Nasara ki misaal aisey hai, jaisey kisi shakhs ne kuchh mazdoor kaam par rakhey aur usney kaha : aadhey din tak eik-eik qirat ke badley mera kaam kon kerega? eik eik qirat ke badley mein yahood ne nisf (aadha) din tak kaam kiya, phir usney kaha : kon hai jo eik eik qirat par merey liye nisf (aadha) din se namaze-Asr tak kaam kerega? Nasara ne nisf (aadhe) din se lekar namaze-Asr tak eik eik qirat par kaam kiya, phir usney kaha : namaze-Asr se ghurub aaftaab tak do-do qirat par merey liye kon kaam kerega? sun lo ! wo tum ho jo namaze-Asr se ghurub aaftaab tak kaam karogey. sun lo ! hamarey liye dugna ajr hai, (us par) yahood aur Nasara naraz ho gaey to unhoney kaha : ham kaam ziyada karen aur ajr aur mazduri kam paeyn, Allah Taala ne farmaya : kya maine tumharey haq mein koi kami ki hai? unhoney arz kiya, nahin, Allah Taala ne farmaya : ye mera Fazal aur meharbani hai main isey jisey chahunga ata karunga.'' Bukhari."
6284,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se mujh se sab se ziyada mohabbat karney waley wo log hain jo merey baad hongey un mein se her eik ye khahish rakhega ke kaash! merey ehle aur ayaal aur merey sarey maal ke badley mein wo mujhey dekh ley.'' rawahu Muslim.
6285,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat mein se eik jamaat Allah ke Deen par qaaim rahegi, unhen be-yaar aur madadgar chhodney wala unhen nuqsan pahuncha sakega na unki mukhalifat karney wala yahan tak ke Allah ka Amr (hukm) (maut ka waqt) aa jaeyga aur wo usi haalat par hongey.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : (ان من عباد اللہ) kitabul qasaas mein zikr ki gaee hai."
6286,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ki misal barish ki tarah hai, malum nahin uskey awwal mein khair hai ya uskey aakhir mein khair hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
6287,"Hazrat Jaafar apney walid se aur apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khush ho jaao , khush ho jaao , meri ummat ki misaal , barish ki tarah hai, malum nahin uskey aakhir mein khair hai ya uskey awwal mein khair hai, ya eik baagh ki tarah hai, is mein se eik saal eik fauj ko khurak di gaee , phir eik saal is mein se eik aur fauj ko khurak di gaee , shayad ke aakhiri fauj pahnaai ke aetbar se ziyada wasee (chaudi) aur gehraai ke lihaz se ziyada gahri ho aur khoobsurti ke aetbar se ziyada Husain ho, wo ummat kaisey halak hogi jiskey shuru mein main hun, Mehdi uskey wast (beech) mein hai aur Masih (Alaihissalam) iskey aakhir mein hai, lekin us doran eik giroh kaj munasib aur tedha hoga wo mujh se hain na main un se hun.'' rawahu rizeen."
6288,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey nazdik kis makhluq ka eman ziyada achchhaa hai? ''unhoney arz kiya : farishton ka, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen kya hai ke wo eman na laeyn jabkey wo apney rab ke paas hain.'' unhoney arz kiya : phir Anbiya (Alaihissalam) , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen kya hai ke wo eman na laeyn halanke un par ""wahi"" nazil hoti hai.'' unhoney arz kiya, phir ham , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen kya hai ke eman na laao jabkey main tumharey darmiyan mojud hun.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya merey nazdik un logon ka eman sab se achchhaa hai jo merey baad hongey, wo sahifey paeyngey un main eik kitab hogi wo uski her chiz par eman laeyngey.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
6289,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Alaa Hizrami bayan kartey hain, mujhey us shakhs ne hadees bayan ki jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''is ummat ke aakhir mein kuchh aisey log hongey jinkey liye unke pehley logon ka sa ajr hoga, wo neki ka hukm karengey, burai se mana karengey aur wo fitney walon se qitaal (jang) karengey.'' Imam Behaqi ne un dono hadeeson ko dalaeelun nubuwa mein riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
6290,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us shakhs ke liye basharat hai jisney (haalate-emaan mein) mujhey dekha aur us shakhs ke liye saat martaba basharat hai jisney mujhey dekha nahin lekin wo mujh par eman laya.'' rawahu Ahmed.
6291,"Hazrat ibne Mahereez (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Sahaba mein se eik aadmi Abu-Jama'a se kaha : hamein eik aisi hadees bayan karen jo aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni ho, unhoney kaha, theek hai, main tumhen eik achchhi si hadees sunata hun, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khana khaya , Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hamarey sath they, unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham mein se bhi koi behtar hai? ham ne Islam qubul kiya aur aap ke sath mil kar jihad kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan wo log jo tumharey baad aaeyngey aur wo mujh par eman laeyngey halanke unhoney mujhey dekha nahin.'' aur Rizeen ne Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) se in alfaz se riwayat kiya hai, unhoney kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! kya koi ham se behtar hai? aakhir hadees tak. rawahu Ahmed, Darmi aur Rizeen."
6292,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Qurra apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ahle-Sham kharab ho jaeyn to phir tum mein (wahan rehney ya us taraf janey mein) koi behtari nahin hogi, meri ummat ka eik giroh hamesha ghalib rahega, unhen be yaaro madadgar chhod deney wala unka koi nuqsan nahin karega yahan tak ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaey.'' ibne Al Madeeni ne farmaya : wo as-haabul hadees hain. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
6293,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ne meri ummat se bhool-chook aur aisey umur (baton) (yani gunahon) se jin par unhen majbur kiya jaey darguzar farmaya hai.'' (rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi sunan al Qubraa).
6294,"Hazrat Behaz bin Hakim (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Allah Taala ke farman : (کُنْتُمْ خَیْرَ اُمَّۃٍ اُخْرِجَتْ لِلنَّاسِ) ''tum behtareen ummat ho, logon ke liye nikaley gaey ho.'' ke barey mein farmatey huey suna : ''tum sattar ummaton ka tamatto (aakhiri hissa) ho, tum Allah Taala ke yahan un sab se behtar aur moazzaz ho.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Darmi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai. rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
